Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.56,0:01:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信美国\N{\fs10}I believe in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.60,0:01:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美国使我发了财\N{\fs10}America has made my fortune
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.73,0:01:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我以美国方式教养我的女儿\N{\fs10}and I raised my daughter in the American fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.84,0:01:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给她自由\N{\fs10}I give her freedom, but
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.01,0:01:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也告诉她永远不要有辱家门\N{\fs10}I taught her never to dishonor her family.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她交了位男友  但不是意大利人\N{\fs10}She found a boyfriend. Not an Italian.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.35,0:01:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她跟他去看电影  深夜才回家\N{\fs10}She went to the movies with him. She stayed out late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.88,0:01:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并没有责骂她\N{\fs10}I didn't protest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.62,0:01:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两个月前他与另一个男孩\N{\fs10}Two months ago, he took her for a drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.82,0:01:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带她去兜风\N{\fs10}with another boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.39,0:01:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们强灌她喝威士忌\N{\fs10}They made her drink whiskey
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后他们想要占她便宜\N{\fs10}and then they tried to take advantage of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.60,0:02:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她抵抗  她保住了名节\N{\fs10}She resisted. She kept her honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于是他们像对动物般的毒打她\N{\fs10}So they beat her like an animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当我到医院时\N{\fs10}When I went to the hospital,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的鼻梁断了\N{\fs10}her nose was broken
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.92,0:02:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她的下巴被打碎了\N{\fs10}her jaw was shattered
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.02,0:02:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须用钢丝绑着才不会掉下来\N{\fs10}held together by wire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她痛得不能哭\N{\fs10}She couldn't even weep because of the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.09,0:02:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我却哭了  我为什么哭呢？\N{\fs10}But I wept. Why did I weep?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我视她如珠如宝\N{\fs10}She was the light of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.64,0:02:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长得很美丽\N{\fs10}Beautiful girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.04,0:02:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在她再也美丽不起来\N{\fs10}Now she will never be beautiful again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思\N{\fs10}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.16,0:03:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我像个守法的美国人一样\N{\fs10}I went to the police
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.36,0:03:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去报警\N{\fs10}like a good American.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.90,0:03:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那两个男孩受到了审判\N{\fs10}These two boys were brought to trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.64,0:03:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法官判他们有期徒刑三年但缓期执行\N{\fs10}Ajudge sentence them to three years in prison and suspend their sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.84,0:03:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,缓期执行\N{\fs10}Suspended sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们当天就没事了\N{\fs10}They went free that very day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我像个傻瓜似的站在法庭中\N{\fs10}I stood in the courtroom like a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.59,0:03:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而那两个混蛋竟朝着我笑\N{\fs10}And those two bastard, they smiled at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.29,0:03:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于是我对我太太说\N{\fs10}Then I said to my wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.86,0:03:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为求公道我们必须去找柯里昂阁下\N{\fs10}''For justice we must go to Don Corleone.''
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.24,0:03:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去报警前为何不先来找我？\N{\fs10}Why did you go to the police? Why didn't you come to me first?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.81,0:03:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要我怎么样？\N{\fs10}What do you want of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.61,0:03:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你尽管吩咐但求你一定要帮我这个忙\N{\fs10}Tell me anything, but do what I beg you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.01,0:03:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮你什么忙？\N{\fs10}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个我办不到\N{\fs10}That I cannot do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要什么我都会给你\N{\fs10}I'll give you anything you ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.22,0:04:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们相识多年\N{\fs10}We've known each other many years, but this is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.02,0:04:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你第一次来找我帮忙\N{\fs10}the first time you ever came to me for counsel or for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我记不起你上次是何时请我到你家去喝咖啡了\N{\fs10}I can't remember the last time that you invited me to your house for a cup of coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.13,0:04:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何况我太太还是你独生女的教母\N{\fs10}even though my wife is godmother to your only child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我坦白说吧\N{\fs10}But let's be frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.27,0:04:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你从来就不想要我的友谊\N{\fs10}You never wanted my friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.10,0:04:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且你怕欠我人情\N{\fs10}and you were afraid to be in my debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.01,0:04:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想卷入是非\N{\fs10}I didn't want to get into trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.44,0:04:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我了解\N{\fs10}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.38,0:04:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在美国发了财\N{\fs10}You found paradise in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.72,0:05:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生意做的很好  生活过的很好\N{\fs10}You had a good trade, made a good living.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有警察和法律保护你\N{\fs10}Police protected you, and there were courts of law.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.56,0:05:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不需要我这种朋友\N{\fs10}So you didn't need a friend like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...\N{\fs10}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你来找我说\N{\fs10}now you come to me and you say
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.27,0:05:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯里昂阁下  请帮我主持公道\N{\fs10}''Don Corleone, give me justice.''
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你对我一点尊重也没有\N{\fs10}But you don't ask with respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你并不把我当朋友\N{\fs10}You don't offer friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你甚至不愿意喊我教父\N{\fs10}You don't even think to call me ''Godfather.''
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在我女儿结婚当天来我家\N{\fs10}Instead, you come into my house on the day my daughter is to be married
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用钱收买我为你杀人\N{\fs10}and you ask me to do murder for money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.99,0:05:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是要求你主持公道\N{\fs10}I ask you for justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.79,0:05:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那不是公道  你女儿还活着\N{\fs10}That is not justice. Your daughter is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.76,0:05:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么让他们像她一样受折磨\N{\fs10}They must suffer then as she suffers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.30,0:05:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我应该付你多少钱？\N{\fs10}How much shall I pay you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.21,0:06:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包纳萨拉\N{\fs10}Bonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.72,0:06:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包纳萨拉\N{\fs10}Bonasera.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.15,0:06:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底我做了什么\N{\fs10}What have I ever done
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你这么的不尊重我\N{\fs10}to make you treat me so disrespectfully?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你以朋友身份来找我\N{\fs10}If you'd come to me in friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么伤害你女儿的杂碎就会受到折磨\N{\fs10}then the scum that ruined your daughter would be suffering this very day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这种诚实人的敌人\N{\fs10}And if, by chance an honest man like yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.63,0:06:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是我的敌人\N{\fs10}should make enemies then they would become my enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.94,0:06:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么  他们就会怕你\N{\fs10}And then they would fear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当我的朋友？\N{\fs10}Be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教父\N{\fs10}Godfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fs10}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他日我或需要你的帮忙\N{\fs10}Someday, and that day may never come
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可能不会有那么一天\N{\fs10}I'll call upon you to do a service for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但在那一天到来之前\N{\fs10}But until that day
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收下这份公道做为小女结婚之礼\N{\fs10}accept this justice as a gift on my daughter's wedding day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.34,0:07:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢  教父  - 别客气\N{\fs10}- Grazie, Godfather. - Prego.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这件事交给... 克里曼沙\N{\fs10}Give this to Clemenza.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.86,0:07:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要用可靠的人头脑清醒的人\N{\fs10}I want reliable people people that aren't going to be carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.50,0:07:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不是谋杀犯  下手别太重\N{\fs10}I mean, we're not murderers in spite of what this undertaker says.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:57.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 麦克在哪？  - 别担心  他一会就来\N{\fs10}- Where's Michael? - What? Don't worry. It's early. He'll be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.33,0:08:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有麦克我不照相\N{\fs10}We're not taking the picture without Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.70,0:08:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待会再拍\N{\fs10}Taking it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 什么事？  - 麦克的事\N{\fs10}- What's the matter, Sonny? - It's Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  巴西尼阁下\N{\fs10}Don Barzini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认得我儿子吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.18,0:09:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保利  让我喝点酒\N{\fs10}Hey, Paulie! Let me have some wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保利  再来点酒\N{\fs10}Paulie! More wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.52,0:09:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你看起来棒极了  - 你是裁判还是什么？\N{\fs10}- You look terrific on the floor. - Are you a dance judge or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闪开吧  到附近晃晃做你的工作\N{\fs10}Go take a walk around the neighborhood. Do your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仙杜拉  帮个忙别让孩子乱跑  好吗？\N{\fs10}Sandra, come on. Do me a favor. Watch the kids. Don't let them run wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.83,0:09:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看好你自己  好吗？\N{\fs10} - You watch yourself, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两三万元小钞  全是现金\N{\fs10}Twenty or thirty grand. In small bills, cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全在那个小丝袋里\N{\fs10}In that little silk purse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果这是我的婚礼我就发财了\N{\fs10}If this were somebody else's wedding... Sfortunato!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.14,0:10:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保利  接住吧\N{\fs10}Hey, Paulie! I got two gobbagool gabagol and a prosciutto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个笨蛋\N{\fs10}Stupid jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？\N{\fs10}Hey, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.90,0:10:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我得回去工作了  - 汤姆\N{\fs10}- Have to go back to work. - Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是婚礼的一部分\N{\fs10}It's part of the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.47,0:10:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有西西里人在女儿结婚那天能拒绝任何的请求\N{\fs10}No Sicilian can refuse any request on his daughter's wedding day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.08,0:11:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯里昂阁下能受邀到贵府深感荣幸\N{\fs10}Don Corleone, I am honored and grateful that you have invited me to your home-
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干什么？滚\N{\fs10}Get outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是私人宴会  快滚\N{\fs10}This is a private party. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么？是我妹妹的婚礼\N{\fs10}What is it? Hey, my sister's wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死的联邦密探什么都不尊重\N{\fs10}Goddamn FBI don't respect nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.94,0:11:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来 过来\N{\fs10}Hey, come here, come here. Come here!There.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.36,0:11:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但最后他获假释去为美国作战\N{\fs10}But towards the end he was paroled to help with the American war effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去六个月他在我的糕饼店做事\N{\fs10}For the last six months, he's been working at my pastry shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.30,0:11:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纳色利  我的朋友我能为你做什么？\N{\fs10}Nazorine, my friend, what can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在战争结束了\N{\fs10}Now that the war is over
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.00,0:12:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这男孩  安索他们要把他遣返意大利\N{\fs10}this boy, Enzo, they want to repatriate him back to Italy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教父  我有个女儿她和安索...\N{\fs10}Godfather, I have a daughter. See, she and Enzo-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.42,0:12:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要安索留在这个国家和你女儿成亲\N{\fs10}You want Enzo to stay in this country and you want your daughter to be married.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么都了解  谢谢\N{\fs10}You understand everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.22,0:12:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈金先生  谢谢\N{\fs10}Mr. Hagen. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待会看看我为你女儿做的结婚蛋糕\N{\fs10}And wait till you see the beautiful wedding cake I made for your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.60,0:12:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么高... 还有一对新人和天使\N{\fs10}Like this, The bride, the groom and the angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这件事我该交给谁去办？\N{\fs10}- Who should I give this job to?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别给我们这个选区\N{\fs10}- Not to our paisan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.45,0:12:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给别地区的犹太籍众议员\N{\fs10}Give it to a Jew congressman in another district.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名单上还有谁？\N{\fs10}Who else is on the list?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  麦克\N{\fs10}Hey, Michael. How are you? Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.01,0:13:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路卡布拉西不在名单上  但他想要见你\N{\fs10}He's not on the list, but Luca Brasi wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:28.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个... 有这个必要吗？\N{\fs10}Is this... is this necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.82,0:13:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没料到会受邀参加婚礼所以要向你致谢\N{\fs10}He didn't expect to be invited to the wedding so he wanted to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fs10}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.60,0:13:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯里昂阁下  在令嫒婚礼这天\N{\fs10}Don Corleone, I am honored and grateful that you have invited me to your home
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.27,0:13:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能受邀到贵府深感荣幸\N{\fs10}on the wedding day of your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.01,0:13:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望他们早生贵子\N{\fs10}And may their first child be a masculine child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.71,0:13:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克\N{\fs10}Michael?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.88,0:13:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边的那个人在自言自语\N{\fs10}That man over there is talking to himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到那边那个吓人的家伙了吗？\N{\fs10}See that scary guy over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.49,0:13:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他很叫人害怕  - 他是谁？叫什么名字？\N{\fs10}He's a very scary guy.Who is he? What's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他叫做路卡布拉西  有时候替家父办事\N{\fs10}His name is Luca Brasi and he helps my father out sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克  等一下  他过来了\N{\fs10}Wait a minute. He's coming over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.33,0:14:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克\N{\fs10}Michael!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆\N{\fs10}Tom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.64,0:14:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你气色好极了\N{\fs10}You look terrific!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家兄汤姆·哈金  这是凯亚·当斯\N{\fs10}My brother Tom Hagen. This is Kay Adams.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.64,0:14:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好  - 你好\N{\fs10}How do you do? Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.24,0:14:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲要见你\N{\fs10}Your father's been asking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.21,0:14:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 幸会  - 幸会\N{\fs10}- Very nice to meet you. - Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.65,0:14:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若他是你哥哥  为何不同姓？\N{\fs10}If he's your brother, why does he have a different name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.29,0:14:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小时候在街上发现汤姆无家可归\N{\fs10}When my brother Sonny was a kid he found Tom Hagen in the street, and he had no home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.56,0:14:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以家父收养了他\N{\fs10}So my father took him in
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从此他就和我们住在一起了\N{\fs10}and he's been with us ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是个好律师\N{\fs10}He's a good lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是西西里人  但我想他会当军师\N{\fs10}Not a Sicilian, but I think he's gonna be consigliere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.64,0:14:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那是什么？  - 那是...\N{\fs10}- What's that? - That's
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是个顾问  在家族中的地位非常重要\N{\fs10}like a counselor, an advisor. Very important to the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:15:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的扁形通心面还好吧？\N{\fs10}You like your lasagna?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.82,0:15:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯里昂阁下\N{\fs10}Don Corleone
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在令嫒的婚礼受到邀请\N{\fs10}I am honored and grateful that you have invited me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深感荣幸与感激\N{\fs10}to your daughter's wedding
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.73,0:15:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在令嫒结婚的当天\N{\fs10}on the day of your daughter's wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.04,0:15:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望他们能早生贵子\N{\fs10}And I hope that their first child be a masculine child.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.34,0:15:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我一点小小的心意\N{\fs10}I pledge my ever-ending loyalty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:38.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 祝福他们俩白头偕老  - 谢谢你  路卡\N{\fs10}For your daughter's bridal purse. Thank you, Luca,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.49,0:15:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最珍贵的朋友\N{\fs10}my most valued friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.92,0:15:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯里昂阁下  我晓得你忙我先告退了\N{\fs10}Don Corleone, I'm gonna leave you now because I know you are busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.73,0:15:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fs10}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.81,0:16:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯里昂夫人\N{\fs10}Signora Corleone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:44.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不...\N{\fs10}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.06,0:17:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科利参议员对不能亲自来致歉\N{\fs10}Senator Cauly apologized for not coming personally
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说你会谅解的\N{\fs10}but said you'd understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:18:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一些法官也一样他们都送了礼物\N{\fs10}Also some of the judges.They've all sent gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.47,0:18:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面是怎么回事？\N{\fs10}What is that outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强尼\N{\fs10}Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你\N{\fs10}I love you. Hey, Johnny, look over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他大老远由加州赶来参加婚礼\N{\fs10}He came all the way from California to come to the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉过你他会来的\N{\fs10}I told you he was going to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.80,0:18:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经两年了  他也许又有麻烦\N{\fs10}- It's been two years. - He's probably in trouble again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是个好教子\N{\fs10}He's a good godson.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强尼...  唱首歌\N{\fs10}Johnny, Johnny! Sing a song!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克你从未告诉我你认得强尼·方亭\N{\fs10}Michael, you never told me you knew Johnny Fontane.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.16,0:19:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你想见他吗  - 当然\N{\fs10}- Sure. You wanna meet him? - Huh? Oh, well, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 家父帮他建立他的事业  - 真的\N{\fs10}- My father helped him with his career. - He did?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.30,0:19:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么做的？\N{\fs10}How?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.44,0:19:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我们先听这首唱  - 不  麦克\N{\fs10}- Let's listen to the song. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.91,0:19:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  麦克  告诉我\N{\fs10}Please, Michael. Tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.91,0:20:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强尼刚出道时和一个乐队领班签了合约\N{\fs10}When Johnny was first starting out.. he was signed to this personal service contract with a big bandleader.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当他走红后  想要解除合约\N{\fs10}And as his career got better and better he wanted to get out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.03,0:20:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强尼是家父的教子\N{\fs10}Now, Johnny is my father's godson
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.66,0:20:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于是家父去见乐队负责人\N{\fs10}and my father went to see this bandleader
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且出一万元要他与强尼解约\N{\fs10}and he offered him $ 10,000 to let Johnny go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.37,0:20:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说不行\N{\fs10}But the bandleader said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二天家父再去见他  只是这次带着路卡布拉西\N{\fs10}So the next day my father went to see him only this time with Luca Brasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个小时之内\N{\fs10}And within an hour,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.75,0:20:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他签了解约书只收了一千元的支票\N{\fs10}he signed a release for a certified check of $ 1,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是怎么办到的？\N{\fs10}How'd he do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.93,0:20:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家父提了个他不能拒绝的条件\N{\fs10}My father made him an offer he couldn't refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么？\N{\fs10}What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.86,0:20:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路卡布拉西用枪顶着他的头\N{\fs10}Luca Brasi held a gun to his head
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.67,0:20:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要是不签字脑袋就会开花\N{\fs10}and my father assured him that either his brains or his signature would be on the contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是真实的故事\N{\fs10}That's a true story.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯  那是我的家庭  不是我\N{\fs10}That's my family, Kay. It's not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会处理的\N{\fs10}I'll take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.28,0:22:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆\N{\fs10}Tom...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫山提诺来我的办公室\N{\fs10}I want you to find Santino. Tell him to come to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.35,0:22:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好吗？弗雷多\N{\fs10}How are you, Fredo?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.32,0:22:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 家兄弗雷多  - 这位是凯亚当斯\N{\fs10}Fredo, my brother Fredo. This is Kay Adams.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好  - 你好吗？\N{\fs10}- Hi. - How ya doin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.40,0:22:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是舍弟麦克  - 玩的愉快吗？\N{\fs10}- This is my brother Mike. - Are you having a good time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.87,0:22:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的朋友？\N{\fs10}Yeah. This is your friend, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.77,0:22:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道该怎么办\N{\fs10}I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的嗓子很虚弱  很虚弱\N{\fs10}My voice is weak. It's weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.95,0:22:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之我若能得到那部戏的角色\N{\fs10}Anyway, if I had this part in the picture you know
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会再次走红的\N{\fs10}it puts me right back up on top again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.49,0:22:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是电影公司的老板不让我演\N{\fs10}But this this man out there, he won't give it to me. The head of the studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.82,0:22:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他叫什么名字？  - 华尔斯\N{\fs10}- What's his name? - Woltz.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.16,0:23:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不肯让我演而且还说门都没有\N{\fs10}He won't give it to me and he says there's no chance, no chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山尼？\N{\fs10}Sonny?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.67,0:23:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山尼？\N{\fs10}Sonny?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山尼？\N{\fs10}Sonny?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.22,0:23:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山尼？你在里面吗？\N{\fs10}Sonny, you in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.08,0:23:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？\N{\fs10}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.15,0:23:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老头子要见你\N{\fs10}The old man wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.12,0:23:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  马上去\N{\fs10}Yeah, one minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.20,0:23:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山尼\N{\fs10}Sonny
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.10,0:23:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个月以前\N{\fs10}A month ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.51,0:23:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他买下这本畅销书的电影版权\N{\fs10}he bought the movie rights to this book.A best-seller.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.44,0:23:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男主角就像是我的写照\N{\fs10}And the main character is a guy just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.85,0:23:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不需要演只要当我自己即可\N{\fs10}Why, I wouldn't even have to act.Just be myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.48,0:23:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但... 教父  我不知该怎么办？\N{\fs10}Oh, Godfather, I don't know what to do. I don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.79,0:24:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要表现得像个男人\N{\fs10}You are gonna to act like a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.99,0:24:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么回事？\N{\fs10}What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.23,0:24:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你在好莱坞学到的？\N{\fs10}Is this how you turned out a Hollywood finocchio
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.46,0:24:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哭的像个女人？\N{\fs10}that cries like a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.03,0:24:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么办？怎么办？\N{\fs10}''What can I do? What can I do?''
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.70,0:24:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算什么鬼话？\N{\fs10}What is that nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.34,0:24:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,岂有此理\N{\fs10}Ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.51,0:24:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你有花时间与家人共聚吗？  - 我当然有\N{\fs10}- You spend time with your family? - Sure I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.81,0:24:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fs10}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.51,0:24:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为不抽空陪家人的男人不是真正的男人\N{\fs10}Because the man who doesn't spend time with his family can never be a real man.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.92,0:24:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来这\N{\fs10}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.86,0:24:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看来糟透了  我要你多吃点\N{\fs10}You look terrible. I want you to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.33,0:24:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好休息\N{\fs10}I want you to rest well, and
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.43,0:24:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从现在起一个月内好莱坞大亨会让你愿望成真\N{\fs10}a month from now this Hollywood big shot's gonna give you what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.80,0:24:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了他们一周内就要开拍了\N{\fs10}Too late. They start shooting in a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.07,0:24:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会给他一个他无法拒绝的提议\N{\fs10}I'm gonna make him an offer he can't refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.87,0:24:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你到外面去好好的玩\N{\fs10}Now just go outside, enjoy yourself and forget about all this nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.18,0:25:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 其他的交给我来办  - 好的\N{\fs10}- Listen. I want you to leave it all to me. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.34,0:25:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我女儿女婿何时离开？\N{\fs10}What time does my daughter leave with the bridegroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.31,0:25:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,切完蛋糕后的几分钟\N{\fs10}In a few minutes, right after they cut the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.72,0:25:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的新女婿要给重要职务吗？\N{\fs10}Now, your new son-in-law, we give him something important.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.29,0:25:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,永远不要\N{\fs10}Never.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.79,0:25:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他们过好日子但别让他插手家族中的事\N{\fs10}Give him a living but never discuss the family business with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.86,0:25:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有什么事？\N{\fs10}What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.99,0:25:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,威尔斯索拉索来过电话\N{\fs10}Virgil Sollozzo called.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.63,0:25:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下周我们必须安排跟他见面\N{\fs10}We have to give him a day sometime next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.60,0:25:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等你从加州回来我们再讨论\N{\fs10}We'll discuss him when you come back from California.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.50,0:25:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我何时要去加州了？\N{\fs10}When am I going to California?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.37,0:25:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你今晚去\N{\fs10}I want you to go tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.10,0:25:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你和这个...\N{\fs10}I want you to talk to this
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.24,0:25:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电影大亨谈谈把强尼的事摆平\N{\fs10}movie big shot and settle this business for Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.34,0:26:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若没有其他事我想去参加我女儿的婚礼了\N{\fs10}If there's nothing else, I'd like to go to my daughter's wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.78,0:26:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛  我们要拍照了\N{\fs10}Carlo, we're gonna take the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.85,0:26:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下\N{\fs10}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.66,0:26:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  麦克  我不行\N{\fs10}No, Michael, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.43,0:26:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  就是这样  别动\N{\fs10}Just a little closer.Okay, that's it. Just like that now. Hold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.21,0:28:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  开始说吧\N{\fs10}All right, start talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.95,0:28:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是强尼·方亭的朋友派来的\N{\fs10}I was sent by a friend of Johnny Fontane.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.25,0:28:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的朋友是我的委托人\N{\fs10}This friend is my client
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.78,0:28:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是华尔斯先生能帮他个小忙\N{\fs10}and would give his undying friendship to Mr. Woltz
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.05,0:28:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他将会感激不尽\N{\fs10}if Mr. Woltz would grant us a small favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.99,0:28:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续说下去\N{\fs10}Woltz is listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.36,0:28:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你下周开拍的新片男主角让强尼担任\N{\fs10}Give Johnny the part in that new war film you're starting next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.10,0:28:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他的朋友会回报我什么好处？\N{\fs10}And what favor would your friend grant Mr. Woltz?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.34,0:28:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你若有工会问题我的委托人能摆平\N{\fs10}You're gonna have some union problems.My client could make them disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.81,0:28:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你旗下一位抽大麻的大牌\N{\fs10}Also, one of your top stars has just moved from
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.55,0:28:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在吸起海洛因了\N{\fs10}marijuana to heroin.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.61,0:28:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想要威胁我吗？\N{\fs10}- Are you trying to muscle me? - Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.98,0:28:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对没有  我只是...\N{\fs10}Absolutely not.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.88,0:28:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着你这个油腔滑调的王八蛋\N{\fs10}Listen to me, you smooth-talking son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.48,0:28:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我对你及你的老板说清楚不管他是何许人\N{\fs10}Let me lay it on the line for you and your boss, whoever he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.02,0:29:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强尼·方亭绝对得不到那个角色\N{\fs10}Johnny Fontane will never get that movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.22,0:29:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎有多少意大利的移民来找我麻烦\N{\fs10}I don't care how many dago, guinea, wop greaseball goombahs come outta the woodwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.66,0:29:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是德裔爱尔兰人\N{\fs10}I'm German-Irish.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.06,0:29:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坦白告诉你  德国朋友\N{\fs10}Well, let me tell you something, my kraut mick friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.70,0:29:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你大祸临头了  你甚至不会晓得是谁扁你\N{\fs10}I'll make so much trouble for you, you won't know what hit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.17,0:29:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,华尔斯先生  我是位律师我不是来威胁你\N{\fs10}I'm a lawyer. I have not threatened-
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.27,0:29:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认识纽约的每位大律师你是谁？\N{\fs10}I know almost every big lawyer in New York. Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.67,0:29:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的执业情况很特别  只为一位委托人办事\N{\fs10}I have a special practice. I handle one client.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.24,0:29:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有我的电话号码  我等你电话\N{\fs10}Now, you have my number. I'll wait for your call.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.98,0:29:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉你  我很喜欢你的电影\N{\fs10}By the way, I admire your pictures very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.79,0:29:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摸清他的底细\N{\fs10}Check him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.78,0:29:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是美极了\N{\fs10}- This is really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.31,0:30:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看这个原本是用来装饰王宫的\N{\fs10} - Look at this.Used to decorate the palace of a king.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.62,0:30:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮\N{\fs10}Oh, yeah. Very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.09,0:30:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为何不说你为柯里昂阁下做事\N{\fs10}Why didn't you say you worked for Corleone, Tom?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.45,0:30:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你只是个市井流氓\N{\fs10}I thought you were just some cheap, two-bit hustler
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.39,0:30:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是强尼派来勒索我的\N{\fs10}Johnny was running in, trying to bluff me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.46,0:30:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非真的必要  否则我不想提起他的名字\N{\fs10}I don't like to use his name unless it's really necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.33,0:30:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你的酒还好吗？  - 很好\N{\fs10}- How's your drink, Tom? - Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.00,0:30:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到这边来  让你看看真正漂亮的东西\N{\fs10}Come with me. I want to show you something really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.83,0:30:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼光应该不错吧？\N{\fs10}You do appreciate beauty, don't you, Tom?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.44,0:30:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里  这匹马价值六十万元\N{\fs10}There you are. $600,000 on four hooves.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.24,0:30:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我敢说俄国沙皇也从未在马身上花那么大笔钱\N{\fs10}I'll bet Russian czars never paid that kind of dough for a single horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.61,0:30:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,达通\N{\fs10}Khartoum.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.85,0:30:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,达通\N{\fs10}Khartoum.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.48,0:30:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我不会用它们来比赛  我要它们当种马\N{\fs10}I'm not gonna race him, though. I'm gonna put him out to stud.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.56,0:30:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢  汤尼  - 不必客气\N{\fs10}- Thanks, Tony. - You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.19,0:30:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们去吃点东西吧\N{\fs10}- Come on. - Let's get something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.86,0:30:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯里昂是强尼的教父\N{\fs10}Mr. Corleone is Johnny's godfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.33,0:30:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对意大利人而言  那是种宗教上神圣的亲密关系\N{\fs10}To the Italian people, that's a very religious sacred, close relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.97,0:30:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很敬重这点\N{\fs10}I respect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.20,0:30:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他除了这件事\N{\fs10}Just tell him he should ask me anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.84,0:31:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都答应\N{\fs10}This is one favor I can't give him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.18,0:31:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他被拒绝一次后不会再要求第二次\N{\fs10}He never asks a second favor when he's been refused the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.65,0:31:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不了解  强尼·方亭永远别想演那部电影\N{\fs10}- Understood? - You don't understand.Johnny Fontane never gets that movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.92,0:31:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他很适合那个角色\N{\fs10}That part is perfect for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.62,0:31:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会让他成为巨星\N{\fs10}It'll make him a big star.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.69,0:31:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我要让他走投无路\N{\fs10}I'm gonna run him out of the business.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.22,0:31:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你为什么\N{\fs10}Let me tell you why.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.86,0:31:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强尼毁了一位华尔斯国际公司最有前途的女星\N{\fs10}Johnny Fontane ruined one of Woltz International's most valuable proteges.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.63,0:31:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五年来我们不断地训练她\N{\fs10}For five years, we had her under training.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.84,0:31:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌唱课  表演课  跳舞课\N{\fs10}Singing lessons, acting lessons, dancing lessons.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.97,0:31:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在她身上投资了无数的金钱\N{\fs10}I spent hundreds of thousands of dollars on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.27,0:31:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要让她成为一位巨星\N{\fs10}I was gonna make her a big star.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.74,0:31:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我更坦白的告诉你\N{\fs10}And let me be even more frank.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.45,0:31:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你知道我不是铁石心肠也不是势利眼\N{\fs10}Just to show you that I'm not a hard-hearted man that it's not all dollars and cents.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.72,0:31:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她年轻漂亮  天真无邪\N{\fs10}She was beautiful. She was young, she was innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.42,0:31:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我拥有她就等于拥有全世界\N{\fs10}She was the greatest piece of ass I've ever had and I've had 'em all over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.79,0:31:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后强尼·方亭出现了\N{\fs10}And then Johnny Fontane comes along with his olive oil
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.03,0:31:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,带着磁性的嗓音加上意大利的魅力\N{\fs10} voice and guinea charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.23,0:32:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把她拐走了\N{\fs10}And she runs off.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.10,0:32:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她跑掉了使我非常难堪\N{\fs10}She threw it all away just to make me look ridiculous
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.31,0:32:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我这种地位的人无法忍受难堪\N{\fs10}and a man in my position can't afford to be made to look ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.61,0:32:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你马上给我滚\N{\fs10}Now you get the hell outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.02,0:32:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是那混球想对我动粗\N{\fs10}And if that goombah tries any rough stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.89,0:32:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉他我不是乐队领班\N{\fs10}you tell him I ain't no bandleader.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.69,0:32:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听过那个故事了\N{\fs10}Yeah. I heard that story.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.53,0:32:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你的晚餐款待\N{\fs10}Thank you for the dinner and a very pleasant evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.60,0:32:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许你能派车送我去机场\N{\fs10}If your car could take me to the airport
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.53,0:32:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯里昂先生坚持坏消息要立刻回报\N{\fs10}Mr. Corleone is a man who insists on hearing bad news immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.78,0:34:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你不会太累吧？汤姆  - 我在飞机上睡过了\N{\fs10}- You're not too tired, Tom? - No, I slept on the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.85,0:34:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这里有索拉索的资料\N{\fs10}I have the Sollozzo notes here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.06,0:34:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,众人皆知  索拉索是土耳其人\N{\fs10}Now Sollozzo is known as ''The Turk.''
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.76,0:34:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他应该善于用刀\N{\fs10}He's supposed to be very good with a knife
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.96,0:34:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但只有发生利益冲突时才会使用\N{\fs10}but only in matters of business with some sort of reasonable complaint.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.47,0:34:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是做毒品生意的\N{\fs10}his business is narcotics.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.54,0:34:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在土耳其种罂粟\N{\fs10}he has fields in Turkey where they grow the poppy
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.28,0:34:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在西西里有工厂提炼成海洛因\N{\fs10}and in Sicily he has the plants to process them into heroin.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.25,0:34:59.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他需要现金\N{\fs10}Now, he needs cash and
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.01,0:35:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及在毒品交易时需要警方的保护\N{\fs10}he needs protection from the police for which he gives a piece of the action.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.85,0:35:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无法查出保护费价钱多少\N{\fs10}I couldn't find out how much.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.79,0:35:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在纽约是塔塔基利亚家族在保护他\N{\fs10}The Tattaglia family is behind him here in New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.76,0:35:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们一定也想分占利益\N{\fs10}Now, they have to be in it for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.79,0:35:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山尼·柯里昂\N{\fs10}Santino Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.26,0:35:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他的犯罪前科呢？  - 一次在意大利  一次在这\N{\fs10}What about his prison record?Two terms, one in Italy, one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.00,0:35:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是众所周知的大毒枭\N{\fs10}He's known as a top narcotics man.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.87,0:35:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山提诺  你认为呢？\N{\fs10}Santino, what do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.20,0:35:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白粉可以赚大钱\N{\fs10}There's a lot of money in that white powder.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.11,0:35:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我赞成  毒品比什么都好赚\N{\fs10}Tom? I say, yes, there's more money potential in narcotics than anything else we're looking at.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.51,0:35:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我们不加入  别人也会\N{\fs10}If we don't get into it, somebody else will.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.32,0:35:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许是五大家族之一也许全部都会\N{\fs10}Maybe one of the five families, maybe all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.52,0:35:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会用毒品赚到的钱买通警方和政客\N{\fs10}With the money they earn they can buy more police and political power.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.92,0:35:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时就会赶上我们\N{\fs10}Then they come after us.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.16,0:35:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们掌握了工会及赌场\N{\fs10}Now we have the unions, we have the gambling
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.99,0:35:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而他们却掌握未来最好的东西毒品\N{\fs10}and they're the best things to have, but narcotics is a thing of the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.63,0:35:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们若不能分一杯羹\N{\fs10}If we don't get a piece of that action
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.33,0:35:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可能会失去一切\N{\fs10}we risk everything we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.77,0:35:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是指现在而是在十年之内\N{\fs10}Not now, but ten years from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.44,0:36:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的答案是什么呢？爸爸\N{\fs10}So? What's your answer gonna be, Pop?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.25,0:36:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯里昂阁下\N{\fs10}Don Corleone,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.02,0:36:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要有势力的友人\N{\fs10}I need a man who has powerful friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.49,0:36:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要一百万元的现金\N{\fs10}I need a million dollars in cash.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.13,0:36:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你手中掌握的政客\N{\fs10}I need those politicians that you carry in your pocket, like nickels and dimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.60,0:36:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 对我家族有什么利益？  - 三成\N{\fs10}- What is the interest for my family? - 30 per cent.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.74,0:36:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一年你就可进帐三四百万元\N{\fs10}In the first year, your end should be 3, 4 million dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.74,0:36:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后还会增加\N{\fs10}And then it would go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.94,0:36:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔塔基利亚家族会得到什么好处？\N{\fs10}And what is the interest for the Tattaglia family?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.42,0:36:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的敬意\N{\fs10}My compliments.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.82,0:36:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会从我那一份当中分给他们\N{\fs10}I'll take care of the Tattaglias outta my share.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.29,0:36:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我提供财务 政治和法律的保护可以分到三成  这就是你想说的\N{\fs10}So, I receive 30% for finance political influence and legal protection.That's what you're telling me
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.03,0:37:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\fs10}-  That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.07,0:37:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为何来找我\N{\fs10}Why do you come to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.54,0:37:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我为何值得你这么慷慨？\N{\fs10}Why do I deserve this generosity?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.04,0:37:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若你能考虑投资一百万元现金\N{\fs10}If you consider a million dollars in cash just finance,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.35,0:37:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就会向你敬礼  柯里昂阁下\N{\fs10}ti saluto, Don Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.19,0:37:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我肯见你是因为我听说你是个正直的人\N{\fs10}I said that I would see you because I heard that you were a serious man
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.46,0:37:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我以礼相待\N{\fs10}to be treated with respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.50,0:37:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我必须拒绝你\N{\fs10}But I must say no to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.84,0:37:42.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会告诉你原因\N{\fs10}And I'll give you my reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.78,0:37:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我是有很多政界的朋友\N{\fs10}It's true, I have a lot of friends in politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.82,0:37:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但若他们知道我在搞毒品生意而不再是赌博时\N{\fs10}But they wouldn't be friendly very long if they knew my business
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.75,0:37:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们就不再是我的朋友\N{\fs10}was drugs instead of gambling
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.49,0:37:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们认为赌博只是些无伤大雅的事业\N{\fs10}which they regard as a harmless vice.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.12,0:37:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但毒品是败坏德性的生意\N{\fs10}- But drugs is a dirty business.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.23,0:37:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 但是柯里昂阁下...   - 对我而言一个人以何为生\N{\fs10}- No, Don Corleone - It doesn't make any difference to me
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.93,0:38:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并没有什么差别\N{\fs10}what a man does for a living, you understand
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.16,0:38:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你这种生意... 有一点危险性\N{\fs10}but your business is a little dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.44,0:38:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若你还是担心安全的问题\N{\fs10}If you're worried about security for your million
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.24,0:38:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔塔基利亚会做保证的\N{\fs10}the Tattaglias will guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.04,0:38:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说塔塔基利亚家族会保证我们的投资...\N{\fs10}You're tellin' me the Tattaglias guarantee our investment-
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.58,0:38:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下\N{\fs10}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.75,0:38:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看我把孩子都给宠坏了\N{\fs10}I have a sentimental weakness for my children and I spoil them, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.46,0:38:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们说话非常没有分寸\N{\fs10}They talk when they should listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.66,0:38:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但总之  索拉索先生\N{\fs10}But anyway Signor Sollozzo,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.26,0:38:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的决定还是不行\N{\fs10}my ''no'' is final
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.46,0:38:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要恭喜你的生意\N{\fs10}and I wish to congratulate you on your new business.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.60,0:38:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你会很成功... 我祝你好运\N{\fs10}I know you'll do very well, and good luck to you
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.07,0:38:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是你的生意不会与我的冲突\N{\fs10}especially since your interests don't conflict with mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.41,0:38:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fs10}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.69,0:39:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山提诺\N{\fs10}Santino.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.53,0:39:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到这来\N{\fs10}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.63,0:39:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么回事？\N{\fs10}What's the matter with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.74,0:39:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你和女孩子胡搞之后脑子退化了\N{\fs10}I think your brain is going soft from all that comedy you're playing with that young girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.47,0:39:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让外人知道你在想什么\N{\fs10}Never tell anybody outside the family what you're thinking again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.91,0:39:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fs10}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.02,0:39:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆  这是什么乱七八糟的？\N{\fs10}Tom, what... what is this nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.72,0:39:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是强尼送的  他主演了那部新电影\N{\fs10}It's from Johnny. He's starring in that new film.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.56,0:39:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  把它拿走\N{\fs10}Well, take it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.06,0:39:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它放到那去\N{\fs10}Take it over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.76,0:39:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有\N{\fs10}And
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.23,0:39:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫路卡布拉西到这来\N{\fs10}tell Luca Brasi to come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.64,0:39:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对这索拉索有点担心\N{\fs10}I'm a little worried about this Sollozzo fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.01,0:39:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你弄清楚他在耍什么把戏\N{\fs10}I want you to find out what he's got under his fingernails, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.95,0:40:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到塔塔基利亚那边去\N{\fs10}Go to the Tattaglias and
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.69,0:40:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让他们以为你与我们家族不融洽\N{\fs10}make them think that you're not too happy with our family
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.29,0:40:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽量查\N{\fs10}and find out what you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.11,0:40:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我买了东西给令堂\N{\fs10}And I got something for your mother and for Sonny
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.51,0:40:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有给弗雷多的领带  给汤姆的钢笔\N{\fs10}and a tie for Freddy and Tom Hagen got the Reynolds pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.59,0:40:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你圣诞节想要什么？  - 我只要你\N{\fs10}- What do you want for Christmas? - Me? Oh, just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.59,0:41:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒醒  弗雷多\N{\fs10}Andiamo, Fredo.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.46,0:41:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫保利备车  我们要走了\N{\fs10}Tell Paulie to get the car. We're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.46,0:41:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  爸\N{\fs10}Okay, Pa.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.06,0:41:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来开车  保利今早生病了\N{\fs10}I'll have to get it myself. Paulie called in sick this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.83,0:41:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保利是个好孩子  我不介意自己开车\N{\fs10}Paulie's a good kid. I don't mind gettin' the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.44,0:41:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fs10}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.22,0:42:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 路卡  我是布诺塔塔基利亚  - 我知道\N{\fs10}- Luca,I am Bruno Tattaglia. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.36,0:42:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想喝杯威士忌吗？\N{\fs10}Scotch?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.06,0:42:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先暖和一下\N{\fs10}Prewar.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.53,0:42:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喝酒
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.66,0:42:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我是谁吗？\N{\fs10}You know who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.20,0:42:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认识你\N{\fs10}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.67,0:42:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和塔塔基利亚家族谈过了对吧？\N{\fs10}You have been talking to the Tattaglia family... right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.71,0:42:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为我们可以一起做些生意\N{\fs10}I think you and I can do business.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.98,0:42:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要像你这么壮的人\N{\fs10}I need someone strong like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.85,0:42:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听说你与柯里昂家族不和\N{\fs10}I heard you are not happy with the Corleone family.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.79,0:42:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想加入我们吗？\N{\fs10}Want to join me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.56,0:42:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能得到什么好处？\N{\fs10}What's in it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.06,0:43:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起薪五万元\N{\fs10}$50,000 to start with.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.33,0:43:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不坏\N{\fs10}Not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.64,0:43:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同意了？\N{\fs10}Agreed?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.63,0:44:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆·哈金  圣诞快乐\N{\fs10}Tom! Tom Hagen. Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.40,0:44:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴遇见你\N{\fs10}I'm glad I run into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.34,0:44:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我想跟你聊聊  - 我没时间\N{\fs10}- I wanna talk to you. - I haven't got time.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.74,0:44:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为我们拨点时间  军师  上车\N{\fs10}Oh, make time, consigliere. Get in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.98,0:44:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你担心什么？\N{\fs10}What are you worried about?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.91,0:44:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想杀你的话你早已死了\N{\fs10}If I wanted to kill you, you'd be dead already.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.08,0:44:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上车\N{\fs10}Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.66,0:44:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍候一下  弗雷多我买点水果\N{\fs10}Fredo, I'm gonna buy some fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.00,0:44:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  爸\N{\fs10}Okay, Pa.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.64,0:44:54.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣诞快乐  我要买些水果\N{\fs10}Hi. Merry Christmas.I want some fruit over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.85,0:45:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个给我 不 是那个\N{\fs10}Gimme three of them.No, that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.34,0:45:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷多\N{\fs10}Fredo!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.59,0:46:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸\N{\fs10}Papa.Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.43,0:46:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克  我若是修女你是否会更喜欢我\N{\fs10}Would you like me better if I were a nun
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.87,0:46:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像小说中的角色你知道吗？\N{\fs10}like in the story, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.54,0:46:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会\N{\fs10}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.67,0:46:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若我是英格丽褒曼你是否会更喜欢我？\N{\fs10}Then would you like me better if I were Ingrid Bergman?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.71,0:46:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个想法不错\N{\fs10}Now that's a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.61,0:46:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克\N{\fs10}Michael.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.65,0:46:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  你若是英格丽褒曼我不会更喜欢你的\N{\fs10}No, I would not like you better if you were Ingrid Bergman.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.48,0:46:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 麦克  - 怎么回事？\N{\fs10}- Mike- - What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.29,0:46:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（维多柯里昂被谋杀）
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.87,0:47:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面没说他是死是活\N{\fs10}They don't say if he's dead or alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.63,0:47:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 山尼  我是麦克  - 麦克  你到哪去了？\N{\fs10}- Sonny, Michael. - Michael, where you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.96,0:47:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他没事吧？  - 我们还不知道\N{\fs10}Is he all right? We don't know yet. There's all kinds of stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.84,0:47:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他伤的很重  麦克\N{\fs10}he was hit bad, Mikey.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.91,0:47:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你还在吗？  - 是的  我在这\N{\fs10}- Are you there? - Yeah, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.67,0:47:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你到哪去了？我很担心  - 汤姆没说我打过电话吗？\N{\fs10}Where you been? I was worried. Didn't Tom tell you? I called.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.68,0:47:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说  回家来你应该在这陪妈妈的\N{\fs10}No. Look, come home, kid. You should be with Mama, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.55,0:47:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fs10}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.96,0:47:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊\N{\fs10}Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.43,0:48:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山尼\N{\fs10}Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.14,0:48:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谁？  - 开门  我是克里曼沙\N{\fs10}- Go. Who is it? - Open up. It's Clemenza.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.45,0:48:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又有你老头的消息了\N{\fs10}There's more news about your old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.38,0:48:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,街头谣传他已经死了\N{\fs10}The word is out on the street he's already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.32,0:48:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是怎么回事？  - 山尼  别激动\N{\fs10}Shut your mouth. What's the matter with you?Jesus Christ! Take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.09,0:48:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保利在哪？\N{\fs10}- Where was Paulie?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.26,0:48:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保利病了  他整个冬天都病了\N{\fs10}- Paulie was out sick. He's been sick all winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.56,0:48:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他病了几次？  - 病了三四次\N{\fs10}- How many times he been sick? - Only maybe three, four times.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.10,0:48:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 弗雷多并不想另找保镖  - 马上接他来\N{\fs10}- I asked Freddy if he wants a different bodyguard.He said no. - Pick him up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.93,0:48:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不管他病的有多重\N{\fs10}I don't care how sick he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.54,0:48:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要他还在呼吸我要你把他带到家父的房子去\N{\fs10}If he's breathin', I want you to bring him to my father's house now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.54,0:48:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在  明白吗？现在\N{\fs10}Understand? Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.07,0:48:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  你要我派人到这边来吗？\N{\fs10}You want me to send people here?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.21,0:48:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用  去吧\N{\fs10}No, just you and him. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.62,0:49:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会派几个人到家里来\N{\fs10}All right.I'm havin' a couple of our people come to the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.76,0:49:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好  - 山尼·柯里昂吗？\N{\fs10}- Hello? - Santino Corleone?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.29,0:49:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我就是  - 汤姆哈金在我们手上\N{\fs10}- Yeah. - We have Tom hagen.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.46,0:49:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约三小时后我们会释放他\N{\fs10}In about three hours, he'll be released with our proposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.93,0:49:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你做任何事之前先听听他说的话\N{\fs10}Listen to everything he has to say before you do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.47,0:49:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,木已成舟\N{\fs10}What's done is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.01,0:49:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先别发怒  好吗？山尼\N{\fs10}And don't lose that famous temper of yours, huh, Sonny?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.14,0:49:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会的  我会等\N{\fs10}No, I'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.13,0:49:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的老板死了\N{\fs10}Your boss is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.93,0:49:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你在家族中是不喜欢动武\N{\fs10}I know you're not in the muscle end of the family
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.40,0:49:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不想要你感到害怕\N{\fs10}so I don't want you to be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.47,0:49:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你帮助柯里昂家族  还有帮我\N{\fs10}I want you to help the Corleones and I want you to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.34,0:49:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接了你约一小时后\N{\fs10}We got him outside his office
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.98,0:50:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们已在他办公室外干掉他了\N{\fs10}about an hour after we picked you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.38,0:50:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧\N{\fs10}Drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.16,0:50:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在全看你的了\N{\fs10}So now it's up to you
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.49,0:50:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我与山尼和平解决一切\N{\fs10}to make the peace between me and Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.93,0:50:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山尼对我的主意很热衷  不是吗？\N{\fs10}Sonny was hot for my deal, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.10,0:50:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且你知道那么做是对的\N{\fs10}And you knew it was the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.17,0:50:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山尼会不惜一切的来追杀你\N{\fs10}Sonny will come after you with everything he's got.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.41,0:50:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那会是他的第一个反应\N{\fs10}That'll be his first reaction, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.71,0:50:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以要你去劝劝他\N{\fs10}That's why you gotta talk some sense into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.68,0:50:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔塔基利亚家族全力支持我\N{\fs10}The Tattaglia family is behind me with all their people.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.18,0:50:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纽约其他的家族也会不惜一切防止全面的战争\N{\fs10}The other New York families will go along with anything that will prevent a full-scale war.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.42,0:50:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们面对现实吧  汤姆\N{\fs10}Let's face it,Tom
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.76,0:50:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们全都尊敬他\N{\fs10}in all due respect
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.13,0:50:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但教父已今非昔比愿他安息\N{\fs10}the Don, rest in peace, was slippin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.66,0:50:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十年前我能对付他吗？\N{\fs10}Ten years ago, could I have gotten to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.50,0:50:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在他已经死了\N{\fs10}Well, now he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.71,0:50:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他死了  汤姆\N{\fs10}He's dead, Tom
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.87,0:51:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么能让他复生\N{\fs10}and nothing can bring him back.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.28,0:51:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你得和山尼谈谈\N{\fs10}So you gotta talk to Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.55,0:51:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也得说服两个大头目泰西欧及肥克里曼沙\N{\fs10}You gotta talk to the caporegimes- that Tessio, that fat Clemenza.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.12,0:51:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是笔好生意  汤姆\N{\fs10}It's good business, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.62,0:51:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我试试看\N{\fs10}I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.06,0:51:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但即使是山尼也阻止不了路卡\N{\fs10}But even Sonny won't be able to call off Luca Brasi.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.50,0:51:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个... 路卡让我来担心\N{\fs10}Yeah. Well-Let me worry about Luca.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.78,0:51:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只管说服山尼\N{\fs10}You just talk to Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.25,0:51:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,及他另外两个兄弟\N{\fs10}And the other two kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.25,0:51:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我尽力而为  - 很好\N{\fs10}- I'll do my best. - Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.19,0:51:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在... 你可以走了\N{\fs10}Now, you can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.53,0:52:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢暴力  汤姆我是个生意人\N{\fs10}I don't like violence, Tom. I'm a businessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.17,0:52:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流血代价太高了\N{\fs10}Blood is a big expense.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.96,0:52:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还活着\N{\fs10}He's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.90,0:52:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们打了他五枪  他还活着\N{\fs10}They hit him with five shots, and he's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.03,0:52:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那对我是件坏事\N{\fs10}Well, that's bad luck for me
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.74,0:52:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若你不能谈成那档事对你也不是好事\N{\fs10}and bad luck for you if you don't make that deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.35,0:53:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令堂在医院陪令尊\N{\fs10}Your mother's over in the hospital with your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.55,0:53:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来他能度过难关谢天谢地\N{\fs10}Looks like he's gonna pull through, thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.22,0:53:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 全是塔塔基利亚家族策划的  - 你认为如何？\N{\fs10}- That's a lot of bad blood. - What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.36,0:53:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教父认为这是设计好的\N{\fs10}It's too far. I think it's too personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.80,0:53:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你要把那些人全杀掉？  - 别插手这件事  麦克\N{\fs10}- You gonna kill all those guys? - Stay out of it, Mickey. Do me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.00,0:53:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,索拉索是关键除掉他一切就好办了\N{\fs10}- Sollozzo's the key. You get rid of him, everything falls into line.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:41.84,0:53:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路卡呢？索拉索认为他可以控制路卡\N{\fs10}What about Luca? Sollozzo didn't seem worried about Luca.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.44,0:53:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fs10}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.34,0:53:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果路卡出卖我们我们就有大麻烦了\N{\fs10}If Luca sold out, we're in a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.98,0:53:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人能与路卡连络上吗？\N{\fs10}Has anyone been able to get in touch with Luca?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.98,0:53:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我试了一整夜  但没有人接\N{\fs10}We've been tryin' all night. He might be shacked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.98,0:53:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克  帮我个忙打电话给路卡\N{\fs10}Mick, Do me a favor. try him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.92,0:53:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他从不在外留宿他每次办完事会立刻回家\N{\fs10}Luca never sleeps over with a broad.He always goes home when he's through.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.92,0:54:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆  你是军师\N{\fs10}Well, Tom, you're consigliere.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.32,0:54:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是老头死了我们该怎么办？\N{\fs10}What do we do if the old man dies, God forbid?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.36,0:54:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们万一失去了老头\N{\fs10}If we lose the old man
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.56,0:54:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就会失去政界的连系\N{\fs10}we lose our political contacts and half our strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.63,0:54:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,纽约其他的家族为了避免长期的战争\N{\fs10}The other New York families might wind up supporting Sollozzo
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.44,0:54:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能会联合支持索拉索\N{\fs10}just to avoid a long destructive war.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.24,0:54:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在是1946年了\N{\fs10}This is almost 1946.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.61,0:54:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人想再流血了\N{\fs10}Nobody wants bloodshed anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.98,0:54:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是令尊死了\N{\fs10}If your father dies
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.05,0:54:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就由你做决定了  山尼\N{\fs10}you'll make the deal, Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.85,0:54:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说来容易  那不是你父亲\N{\fs10}That's easy for you to say. He's not your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.59,0:54:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我与你跟麦克对他来说都是儿子\N{\fs10}I was as much a son to him as you or Mike.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.36,0:54:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？\N{\fs10}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.96,0:54:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保利  我叫你在外面守着\N{\fs10}Hey, Paulie, I thought I told you to stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.20,0:54:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大门的人说收到一包东西\N{\fs10}The guy at the gates, they say they got a package.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.90,0:54:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰西欧  去看看是什么\N{\fs10}Yeah? Tessio, go see what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.94,0:54:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要我留在这？\N{\fs10}You want me to hang around?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.14,0:54:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  留在这  你还好吧？\N{\fs10}- Yeah, hang around.- You all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.24,0:54:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我很好\N{\fs10}Yeah,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.38,0:54:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点吃的  你饿了吗？\N{\fs10}Yeah? There's some food in the icebox. You hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.38,0:54:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  没关系的\N{\fs10}No, it's all right. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.55,0:55:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝杯酒吧  一点白兰地能让你舒服点\N{\fs10}- How 'bout a little brandy?- That's good to sweat it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:01.45,0:55:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好吧  - 去吧  孩子\N{\fs10}- Sure. - Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.58,0:55:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那或许是个好主意\N{\fs10}That might be a good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.42,0:55:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你立刻处置那个王八蛋\N{\fs10}I want you to take care of that son of a bitch right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.79,0:55:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保利出卖了老头  那个混蛋\N{\fs10}Paulie sold out the old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.36,0:55:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再见到他\N{\fs10}I don't wanna see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.66,0:55:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你第一件先要解决的工作\N{\fs10}Make that first thing on your list.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.79,0:55:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 明白吗？  - 明白\N{\fs10}- Understand? - Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.23,0:55:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克  明天你带几个人...\N{\fs10}Hey, Mickey, tomorrow you get a couple of guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.27,0:55:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到路卡的公寓去看看等他出现\N{\fs10}Go to Luca's apartment. Wait for him to show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.20,0:55:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们不该让麦克太直接涉入\N{\fs10}Maybe we shouldn't get Mike mixed up in this too directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.87,0:55:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说... 待在家里接电话那会有大帮助的\N{\fs10}Listen, hang around the house on the phone. It'll be a big help.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.24,0:55:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再试着打给路卡\N{\fs10}Try Luca again. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.26,0:55:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 这是什么？  - 那是西西里人的口信\N{\fs10}- What the hell is this? - It's a Sicilian message.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.16,0:55:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那表示路卡布拉西与鱼同眠了\N{\fs10}It means Luca Brasi sleeps with the fishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.78,0:56:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我现在要走了  - 你今晚几点会回家？\N{\fs10}- I'm goin' now. - What time you gonna be home?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.08,0:56:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  也许会很晚\N{\fs10}I don't know. Probably late.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.15,0:56:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别忘了油饼  - 知道了\N{\fs10}- Don't forget the cannoli. - Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.02,0:56:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罗可  坐到另一边去\N{\fs10}Rocco, sit on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.66,0:56:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你挡住后照镜了\N{\fs10}You block the rearview mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:19.76,0:56:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始大发雷霆了\N{\fs10}Sonny's runnin' wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.60,0:56:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想要跟对手开战了\N{\fs10}He's thinkin' of goin' to the mattresses already.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.53,0:56:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们得在西区找个地方藏匿\N{\fs10}We gotta find a spot over on the West Side.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.33,0:56:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你试试西43街309号\N{\fs10}We'll try 309 West 43rd Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.57,0:56:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你知道西区有何好地方吗？  - 我想想看\N{\fs10}- You know any good spots on the West Side? - Yeah, I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.21,0:56:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你开车的时候想想好吗？\N{\fs10}- Think while you're drivin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.71,0:56:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这个月要找一天到纽约去\N{\fs10}I wanna hit New York sometime this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.98,0:56:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒车出去时留意小孩子\N{\fs10}And watch out for the kids when you're backin' out.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.59,0:56:51.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保利  我要你到39街去\N{\fs10}Paulie, I want you to go down 39th Street. Colosanto's.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.99,0:56:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去买18个垫子\N{\fs10}Pick up 18 mattresses for the guys to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.16,0:56:55.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后把帐单拿给我\N{\fs10}Bring me the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.83,0:56:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确定要干净的\N{\fs10}- Yeah, all right. - Make sure they're clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.50,0:57:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们要在那待段长时间\N{\fs10}Those guys are gonna be stuck up in there for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.03,0:57:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它们是干净的  他们说消毒过\N{\fs10}They're clean. They told me they exterminate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.50,0:57:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消毒  用那个字很不好\N{\fs10}''Exterminate''? That's a bad word to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.47,0:57:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消毒  听听这个家伙\N{\fs10}Exterminate. Get this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.01,0:57:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心点  我们才不会为你消毒\N{\fs10}See how we don't exterminate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.88,0:57:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真是好笑\N{\fs10}- Youse funny, or what? - Hey, Paulie?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.15,0:57:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停到路旁去好吗？我要小便\N{\fs10}Pull over.I gotta take a leak.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.73,0:58:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把枪留下\N{\fs10}Leave the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.76,0:58:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把油饼给我\N{\fs10}Take the cannoli.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.05,0:58:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克...\N{\fs10}Hey, Mike!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.66,0:58:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦?\N{\fs10}{\fs10}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.82,0:58:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的电话\N{\fs10}You're wanted on the telephone.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.26,0:58:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是谁？  - 女孩子\N{\fs10}- Who is it? - It's some girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.87,0:58:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你好  凯  - 令尊还好吗？\N{\fs10}- Hello, Kay? - How's your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.27,0:58:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他很好  他能活过来\N{\fs10}He's good. He's gonna make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.91,0:58:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你\N{\fs10}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.98,0:58:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你\N{\fs10}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.58,0:58:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 麦克  - 是  我知道\N{\fs10}- Michael? - Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.15,0:58:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我你爱我\N{\fs10}Tell me you love me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.92,0:58:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能说\N{\fs10}I can't talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.25,0:58:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能说吗？\N{\fs10}Can't you say it?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.25,0:59:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们今晚见\N{\fs10}Yeah, I'll see you tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.02,0:59:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克  你为何不说你爱她\N{\fs10}Why don't you tell that nice girl you love her?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.09,0:59:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我全心全意的爱你\N{\fs10}I love you with all o' my heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.96,0:59:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我若不快点见到你  我会死的\N{\fs10}If I don't see you again a-soon, I'm-a gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.87,0:59:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到这来  孩子  学点东西\N{\fs10}Come over here, kid. Learn somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.73,0:59:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天你也许得为20个男人煮饭\N{\fs10}You might have to cook for 20 guys someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.94,0:59:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一开始先倒点油  炸大蒜\N{\fs10}You see? You start out with a little bit of oil.Then you fry some garlic.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.67,0:59:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后放番茄  炒一下\N{\fs10}Then you throw in some tomatoes, some tomato paste.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.11,0:59:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让它粘锅底\N{\fs10}You fry it. You make sure it doesn't stick.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.18,0:59:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,煮开了之后  加入香肠及肉丸\N{\fs10}When you got it to a boil, shove in all your sausage and meatballs.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.35,0:59:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加一点点酒\N{\fs10}And a little bit of wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.73,0:59:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及...\N{\fs10}And
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.16,0:59:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点点糖\N{\fs10}a little bit of sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.16,0:59:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的秘方\N{\fs10}And that's my trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.30,0:59:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你别说废话了\N{\fs10}Why don't you cut the crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.56,0:59:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有更重要的事要让你去做\N{\fs10}I got more important things for you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.63,0:59:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保利呢？\N{\fs10}How's Paulie?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.77,0:59:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保利  你再也见不到他了\N{\fs10}Won't see him no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.14,0:59:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪？\N{\fs10}Where you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.37,0:59:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到城里去\N{\fs10}To the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.51,0:59:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派保镖跟他一起去\N{\fs10}Send some bodyguards with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.77,0:59:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是去医院看爸爸\N{\fs10}I'm just going to see Pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.41,0:59:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不管  派人跟他一起去\N{\fs10}Send somebody with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.64,0:59:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不会有事的  索拉索知道他是''平民''\N{\fs10}He'll be all right. Sollozzo knows he's a civilian.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.45,1:00:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 小心点  - 是的\N{\fs10}- All right. Be careful, huh? - Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.05,1:00:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是派人跟他一起去\N{\fs10}Send somebody with him anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.88,1:00:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我得走了  - 我能与你一起去吗？\N{\fs10}I have to go.Can I go with you?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.22,1:00:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  凯  那里有刑警还有记者\N{\fs10}No, Kay. There's gonna be detectives there.People from the press.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.96,1:00:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在车上等你\N{\fs10}I'll ride in a cab.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.46,1:00:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要你卷入这件事\N{\fs10}I don't want you to get involved.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.80,1:00:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我何时能再见到你？\N{\fs10}When will I see you again?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.38,1:01:05.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回新罕布夏去\N{\fs10}Go back to New Hampshire
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.58,1:01:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打电话去你父母家找你\N{\fs10}and I'll call you at your parents' house.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.22,1:01:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我何时才能再见到你？麦克\N{\fs10}When will I see you again, Michael?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.12,1:01:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fs10}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.09,1:03:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里干什么？\N{\fs10}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.55,1:03:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不是探病时间\N{\fs10}You're not supposed to be here now.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.92,1:03:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是麦克柯里昂\N{\fs10}I'm Michael Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.13,1:03:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是家父\N{\fs10}This is my father.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.76,1:03:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里没人  守卫到哪去了？\N{\fs10}There's nobody here. What happened to the guards?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.40,1:03:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令尊访客太多妨碍了医院的作业\N{\fs10}Your father just had too many visitors.They interfered with hospital service.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:42.50,1:03:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察在十分钟前要他们离去了\N{\fs10}The police made them leave about ten minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.48,1:03:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请帮我接长滩45620\N{\fs10}Get me Long Beach 4-5-6-2-0, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.98,1:03:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,护士  等一下  先别走\N{\fs10}Nurse, wait a minute. Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.29,1:04:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山尼  我是麦克  我在医院\N{\fs10}Sonny, Michael. I'm at the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.59,1:04:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着  我很晚才到这儿这没有人\N{\fs10}Listen. I got here late. There's nobody here.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.26,1:04:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰西欧的人不在也没有刑警  没有人\N{\fs10}Nobody. No Tessio's men, no detectives, nobody.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.46,1:04:12.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸单独一个人在这\N{\fs10}- Pop is all alone. - Don't panic. We'll send somebody.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.58,1:04:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别惊慌  - 我不会惊慌\N{\fs10}- Don't panic. - I won't panic.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.64,1:04:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉  但你必须离去\N{\fs10}I'm sorry, but you will have to leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.24,1:04:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你帮我把家父移去另一间房\N{\fs10}You and I are gonna move my father to another room.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.98,1:04:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你是否能把这个拆开\N{\fs10}Can you disconnect those tubes
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.58,1:04:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来推病床\N{\fs10}so we can move the bed out?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.18,1:04:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 那是不可能的  - 你认识家父吗？\N{\fs10}- That's out of the question. - Do you know my father?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.68,1:04:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会来杀了他  懂吗？\N{\fs10}Men are coming here to kill him.You understand?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.16,1:04:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在请你帮我忙\N{\fs10}Now, help me, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.10,1:05:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是谁？  - 我是安索  那个糕饼师\N{\fs10}- Who are you? - I am Enzo- the baker.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.84,1:06:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你还记得我吧？  - 安索\N{\fs10}- You remember me? - Enzo?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.11,1:06:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我是安索\N{\fs10}Yes, Enzo.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.21,1:06:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最好离开这  安索这里会有麻烦\N{\fs10}You better get out of here, Enzo.There's gonna be trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.21,1:06:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是有麻烦  我留在这帮你\N{\fs10}If there is trouble, I stay here to help you-
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.71,1:06:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了令尊\N{\fs10}For your father. For your father.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.25,1:06:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  听我说\N{\fs10}All right, listen.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.05,1:06:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在医院大门外面等我  好吗？\N{\fs10}Wait for me outside, in front of the hospital.All right?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.02,1:06:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上出来  快去\N{\fs10}I'll be out in a minute. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:17.86,1:06:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的...\N{\fs10}OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.00,1:06:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好休息吧  爸\N{\fs10}Just lie here, Pop.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.44,1:06:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会照料你的\N{\fs10}I'll take care of you now.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:37.54,1:06:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你在一起\N{\fs10}I'm with you now.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.28,1:07:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把这个丢掉\N{\fs10}Get rid of these.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.72,1:07:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到这来\N{\fs10}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.52,1:07:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把手放在口袋里就像你有把枪\N{\fs10}Put your hand in your pocket like you have a gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.29,1:07:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会有事的\N{\fs10}You'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:31.83,1:07:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会有事的\N{\fs10}You'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.28,1:08:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你做的很好\N{\fs10}You did good.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.75,1:08:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是干什么？\N{\fs10}What's this for?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.43,1:09:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为把你们这些混混全关住了\N{\fs10}I thought I got all you guinea hoods locked up.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.40,1:09:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里干什么？\N{\fs10}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.66,1:09:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守家父的人是怎么回事？\N{\fs10}What happened to the men who were guarding my father, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.90,1:09:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个小混蛋  竟敢管我的事\N{\fs10}Why, you little punk. Don't you tell me my business!
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.37,1:09:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我把那些人全赶走的\N{\fs10}I pulled them guys off of here.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.47,1:09:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你马上离开这医院\N{\fs10}You get out of here and stay away from this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.48,1:09:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非你派人守护家父否则我不会走\N{\fs10}I'm not moving until you put some guards around my father's room.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.11,1:09:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲尔  把他带回去\N{\fs10}Phil, take him in.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.08,1:09:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是清白的  队长\N{\fs10}The kid's clean, Captain. He's a war hero.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.65,1:09:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是个服役荣归的英雄从未和黑手党混在一起\N{\fs10}- He's a war hero. He's never been...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.78,1:09:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死的  我说把他带回去\N{\fs10}Goddamn it, I said take him in.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.69,1:09:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,索拉索付你多少钱来陷害家父？\N{\fs10}What's the Turk paying you to set up my father, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.36,1:09:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他抓牢  让他站稳\N{\fs10}Take ahold of him. Stand him up. Stand him up straight.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.89,1:10:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是柯里昂家的律师\N{\fs10}I'm the attorney for the Corleone family.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.95,1:10:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些人是私家侦探\N{\fs10}These men are private detectives hired
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.49,1:10:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雇来保护维多柯里昂的\N{\fs10}to protect Vito Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.59,1:10:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们有携带武器的执照\N{\fs10}They're licensed to carry firearms.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.99,1:10:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是你干预  我们明早法庭见\N{\fs10}If you interfere, you'll have to appear before a judge in the morning and show cause.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.70,1:10:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  让他走\N{\fs10}All right, let him go.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:22.20,1:10:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fs10}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:53.03,1:10:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些新面孔是怎么回事？\N{\fs10}What's with all the new faces?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:55.17,1:10:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在需要他们\N{\fs10}Gonna need 'em now.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:57.04,1:10:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经过医院的事之后山尼气疯了\N{\fs10}After the hospital thing, Sonny got mad.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.14,1:11:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们今晨四点干掉了布诺塔塔基利亚\N{\fs10}We hit Bruno Tattaglia at 4:00 this morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.24,1:11:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老天爷\N{\fs10}Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.12,1:11:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里看起来像是座城堡\N{\fs10}Looks like a fortress around here.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.96,1:11:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,街上一天24小时都有一百个枪手在巡逻\N{\fs10}A hundred button men on the street, 24 hours a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.03,1:11:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那土耳其人敢露出一根汗毛就挂了\N{\fs10}That Turk shows one hair on his ass, he's dead. Believe me.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:28.73,1:11:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克  到这里来  让我看看你\N{\fs10}Hey, Michael, come here. Let me look at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.84,1:11:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你漂亮极了  漂亮极了\N{\fs10}You look beautiful. Just beautiful. You're gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.98,1:11:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们听我说\N{\fs10}Hey, listen to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.25,1:11:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那土耳其人想谈判\N{\fs10}The Turk, he wants to talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.95,1:11:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那王八蛋紧张了\N{\fs10}Imagine the nerve on this son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.72,1:11:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚整我们  今天想和谈\N{\fs10}Craps out last night, he wants a meeting today.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.02,1:11:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他怎么说？  - 他怎么说？\N{\fs10}- What'd he say? - What did he say?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.32,1:11:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要我们派麦克去\N{\fs10}He wants us to send Michael to hear the proposition.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.32,1:11:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并保证那条件好到我们不会拒绝\N{\fs10}And the promise is that the deal is so good that we can't refuse.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.96,1:11:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那布诺塔塔基利亚呢？\N{\fs10}What about Bruno Tattaglia?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.56,1:11:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是条件的一部分\N{\fs10}That's part of the deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.10,1:12:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他作为对家父挨枪的补偿\N{\fs10}Bruno cancels out what they did to my father.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.27,1:12:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山尼  我们该听听他们怎么说\N{\fs10}Sonny, we ought to hear what they have to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.17,1:12:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  不再听了  军师\N{\fs10}No more. Not this time, Consigliere.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.77,1:12:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不再和谈  不再讨论不再上索拉索的当\N{\fs10}No more meetings, no discussions, no more Sollozzo tricks.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.38,1:12:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去跟他们说  我要索拉索\N{\fs10}You give them one message- I want Sollozzo.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.34,1:12:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则我们就开战\N{\fs10}If not, it's all-out war. We go to the mattresses.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.58,1:12:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山尼  其他家族不会支持的\N{\fs10}Some of the other families won't sit still for a war.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.85,1:12:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫他们把索拉索交给我\N{\fs10}- Then they hand me Sollozzo. - Your father wouldn't like this.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.48,1:12:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山尼  令尊不会喜欢的这是生意  不能感情用事\N{\fs10}This is business, not personal.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.25,1:12:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我父亲就该挨枪了？\N{\fs10}They shot my father.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.45,1:12:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是令尊挨枪也是生意\N{\fs10}Even shooting your father was business,
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.99,1:12:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是个人的事  山尼\N{\fs10}not personal, Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.26,1:12:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那生意必须要停  行吗？\N{\fs10}Well, then business will have to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.22,1:12:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着  帮我个忙  汤姆\N{\fs10}And do me a favor, Tom-
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.76,1:12:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再建议我如何让事情过去\N{\fs10}No more advice on how to patch things up.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.03,1:12:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要帮我赢  好吗？\N{\fs10}Just help me win, please. All right?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.50,1:12:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我查出了打断麦克下巴那麦克劳斯基队长的事\N{\fs10}I found out about this McCluskey who broke Mike's jaw.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.11,1:12:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他怎么样？\N{\fs10}What about him?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.44,1:12:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他肯定在索拉索的规费名单中  而且是很大一笔钱\N{\fs10}He's definitely on Sollozzo's payroll, and for big money.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.84,1:12:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克劳斯基是索拉索的保镖\N{\fs10}McCluskey has agreed to be the Turk's bodyguard.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.85,1:12:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须要了解  山尼\N{\fs10}What you have to understand, Sonny
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.85,1:12:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当索拉索跟警察队长勾搭上时\N{\fs10}is that while Sollozzo's being guarded like this
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.08,1:12:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没人可以碰他了\N{\fs10}he is invulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.72,1:12:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去从没人胆敢干掉纽约警官\N{\fs10}Nobody has ever gunned down a New York police captain. Never.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.52,1:12:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那会是个大灾难\N{\fs10}It would be disastrous.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:58.66,1:13:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有五大家族都会追杀你  山尼\N{\fs10}All the five families would come after you.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.63,1:13:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯里昂家族会被孤立\N{\fs10}The Corleone family would be outcast.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.50,1:13:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使是老头的政治保护都会消失\N{\fs10}Even the old man's political protection would run for cover.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.67,1:13:09.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你\N{\fs10}So do me a favor.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:10.94,1:13:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别轻举妄动\N{\fs10}Take this into consideration.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.41,1:13:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我们等\N{\fs10}All right, we'll wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:23.75,1:13:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能等\N{\fs10}We can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:25.82,1:13:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能等\N{\fs10}Can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:27.92,1:13:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管索拉索答应什么  他会杀了爸爸的\N{\fs10}I don't care what Sollozzo says about a deal.He's gonna kill Pop. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.96,1:13:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是他的关键\N{\fs10}That's the key for him.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.86,1:13:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须干掉索拉索\N{\fs10}Got to get Sollozzo.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:35.89,1:13:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克说的对\N{\fs10}Mike is right.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.86,1:13:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个谈判就没有必要了\N{\fs10}Let me ask you something first.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.23,1:13:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个麦克劳斯基呢？\N{\fs10}What about this McCluskey?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.00,1:13:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要拿这个条子怎么办？\N{\fs10}What do we do with this cop?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:49.98,1:13:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们想跟我见面  对吧？\N{\fs10}They want to have a meeting with me, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.88,1:13:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那会是我 麦克劳斯基及索拉索\N{\fs10}It will be me McCluskey and Sollozzo.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.09,1:14:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们来安排这次会面\N{\fs10}Let's set the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.32,1:14:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们查清楚见面地点在哪里\N{\fs10}Get our informers to find out where it's going to be held.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.93,1:14:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,必须是公开场所  酒吧或餐厅\N{\fs10}We insist it's a public place- a bar, a restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.73,1:14:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人多的地方对我比较安全\N{\fs10}Someplace where there's people, so I feel safe.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.24,1:14:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我与他们一见面他们会搜身  对吧\N{\fs10}They're gonna search me when I first meet them, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.38,1:14:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我身上不能有武器\N{\fs10}So I can't have a weapon on me then.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.01,1:14:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若克里曼沙能想出一个办法\N{\fs10}But if Clemenza can figure a way
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.78,1:14:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能预先把武器放在那\N{\fs10}to have a weapon planted there for me
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.02,1:14:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我就能杀了他们两个\N{\fs10}then I'll kill them both.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.21,1:14:55.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎么做？乖乖的大学生\N{\fs10}What are you gonna do? Nice college boy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.11,1:14:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是不想和家族中的事混在一块吗？\N{\fs10}Didn't want to get mixed up in the family business.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.64,1:15:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在因为他打了你你就想干掉他？\N{\fs10}Now you want to gun down a police captain?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.81,1:15:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这里是什么？军队吗？\N{\fs10}Why? 'Cause he slapped you in the face a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.98,1:15:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一哩以外开枪打他们？\N{\fs10}Do you think this is the army, where you shoot them a mile away?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.25,1:15:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你必须离这么近  砰一声\N{\fs10}You gotta get up close, like this and-
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.12,1:15:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们的脑浆会溅到你身上\N{\fs10}You blow their brains all over your nice Ivy League suit. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.19,1:15:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 山尼...   - 你太感情用事了\N{\fs10}You're taking this very personal.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.72,1:15:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆  这是公事而他却感情用事\N{\fs10}Tom, this is business, and this man is taking it very, very personal.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.23,1:15:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁说不能杀条子的？\N{\fs10}Where does it say you can't kill a cop?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:17.93,1:15:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 别这样  麦克  - 汤姆  慢着\N{\fs10}- Come on, Mikey. - Tom, wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.90,1:15:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是个跟毒品买卖有关的条子\N{\fs10}I'm talking about a cop that's mixed up in drugs.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.77,1:15:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是个不诚实的条子\N{\fs10}I'm talking about a dishonest cop, a crooked cop
Dialogue: 0,1:15:25.84,1:15:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和毒贩混在一起终于得到报应\N{\fs10}who got mixed up in the rackets and got what was coming to him.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:30.31,1:15:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是个好极了的故事\N{\fs10}That's a terrific story.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:32.11,1:15:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,报社不是有我们的人吗？\N{\fs10}We have newspaper people on the payroll, don't we, Tom?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:36.25,1:15:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们也许对那故事有兴趣\N{\fs10}They might like a story like that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.48,1:15:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们也许  只是也许\N{\fs10}They might. They just might.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:43.82,1:15:47.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是感情用事  山尼  纯粹是公事\N{\fs10}It's not personal, Sonny. It's strictly business.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.43,1:15:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做过表面处理了  追踪不到的\N{\fs10}It's as cold as they come. Impossible to trace,
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.23,1:15:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心指纹\N{\fs10}so you don't worry about prints, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.70,1:15:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在扳机和手把上贴了特殊胶布\N{\fs10}I put a special tape on the trigger and the butt.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.50,1:16:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来  试试看\N{\fs10}Here. Try it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.12,1:16:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？扳机太紧了？\N{\fs10}What's the matter, the trigger too tight?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.56,1:16:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的耳朵好辛苦\N{\fs10}- My ears. - I left it noisy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.69,1:16:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没安装消声器那样才能吓走旁观的人\N{\fs10}That way it scares pain-in-the-ass innocent bystanders away.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.70,1:16:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你杀了他们两个\N{\fs10}All right, you shot them both.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.83,1:16:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来你怎么办？\N{\fs10}Now what do you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.60,1:16:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐下吃完我的晚餐\N{\fs10}Sit down, finish my dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.00,1:16:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑\N{\fs10}Come on, kid. Don't fool around.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.64,1:16:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就让你的手垂下  让枪滑掉\N{\fs10}Just let your hand drop to your side and let the gun slip out.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.24,1:16:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都认为你还拿着枪\N{\fs10}Everybody will still think you got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.44,1:16:41.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会瞪着你的脸  麦克\N{\fs10}They're gonna be staring at your face, Mike
Dialogue: 0,1:16:41.68,1:16:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以快步离开那地方但不要跑\N{\fs10}so walk out of the place real fast, but you don't run.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.75,1:16:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别直视任何人但也不要看其他地方\N{\fs10}Don't look nobody directly in the eye, but don't look away, either.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.19,1:16:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们会怕的不敢瞪你  相信我  不必担心\N{\fs10}They're gonna be scared stiff of you, believe me so don't worry about nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.86,1:16:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你若可以全身而退\N{\fs10}You know, you're gonna turn out all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:55.69,1:16:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以休个长假  到哪里都可以\N{\fs10}You take a long vacation, nobody knows where
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.20,1:16:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我们会处理善后\N{\fs10}and we're gonna catch the hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.83,1:17:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你认为后果会有多糟？  - 他妈的蛮糟的\N{\fs10}How bad do you think it's gonna be? Pretty goddamn bad.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.77,1:17:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能所有的家族会联合对付我们\N{\fs10}Probably all the other families will line up against us.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.71,1:17:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那没关系的\N{\fs10}That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.94,1:17:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每五年或十年都会发生一次\N{\fs10}These things gotta happen every five years or so. Ten years.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.28,1:17:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害群之马必须要除掉\N{\fs10}Helps to get rid of the bad blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:13.98,1:17:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上一次到现在已有十年了\N{\fs10}Been ten years since the last one.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.45,1:17:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要先发制人\N{\fs10}You gotta stop them at the beginning
Dialogue: 0,1:17:18.28,1:17:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像要在慕尼黑制止希特勒一样\N{\fs10}like they should have stopped Hitler at Munich.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.42,1:17:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们容忍了希特勒  麻烦就大了\N{\fs10}They should have never let him get away with that.They was just asking for big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.26,1:17:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗？麦克\N{\fs10}You know, Mike,
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.73,1:17:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都以你为荣  你是个英雄\N{\fs10}we was all proud of you being a hero and all.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.83,1:17:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲也是\N{\fs10}Your father too.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.74,1:18:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何线索  什么都没有\N{\fs10}Nothing. Not a hint. Absolutely nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.14,1:18:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,索拉索的人也不知在哪里会面\N{\fs10}Even Sollozzo's people don't know where the meeting will be held.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.44,1:18:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有多少时间？\N{\fs10}How much time do we have?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.38,1:18:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一小时半以后他们在达西路口接你上车\N{\fs10}in an hour and a half- exactly an hour and a half.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.59,1:18:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们派个人追踪他们\N{\fs10}We could put a tail on them, see how it turns out.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.02,1:18:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,索拉索会在街上乱转甩掉我们的人\N{\fs10}Sollozzo'll lose our ass going around the block.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.66,1:18:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来找我们谈判的人呢？\N{\fs10}What about the negotiator?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.53,1:18:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在那边和我的手下玩纸牌\N{\fs10}He's over at my place playing pinochle with a couple of my men.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.43,1:18:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他很高兴  我们在让他赢\N{\fs10}He's happy. They're letting him win.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.57,1:18:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对麦克太危险了\N{\fs10}It's too much of a risk for Mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.90,1:18:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山尼  也许我们该取消\N{\fs10}Maybe we ought to call it off.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.37,1:18:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要麦克平安回来\N{\fs10}The negotiator keeps playing cards
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.24,1:18:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们才会让那个人走的\N{\fs10}until Mike's back safe and sound.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.17,1:18:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何不干脆干掉车上的人呢？\N{\fs10}Why doesn't he blast who's ever in the goddamn car?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.34,1:18:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太危险了  他们会注意的\N{\fs10}Too dangerous. They'll be looking for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.08,1:18:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,索拉索也许根本就不在车上\N{\fs10}Sollozzo might not even be in the car, Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.58,1:18:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来接\N{\fs10}I got it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.37,1:19:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布朗区的路易士餐厅\N{\fs10}Louis Restaurant in the Bronx.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.68,1:19:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可靠吗？\N{\fs10}Is it reliable?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.84,1:19:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克劳斯基的分局里有我的人\N{\fs10}That's my man in McCluskey's precinct.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.81,1:19:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长必须24小时待命\N{\fs10}A police captain's got to be on call 24 hours a day.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.58,1:19:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他八点到十点会去那里\N{\fs10}He signed out at that number between 8:00 and 10:00.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.75,1:19:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有谁知道那个地方\N{\fs10}Anybody know this joint?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.09,1:19:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fs10}Yeah, sure. I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.39,1:19:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我们太理想了\N{\fs10}It's perfect for us.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.86,1:19:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家庭餐厅  食物精美\N{\fs10}A small family place, good food.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.03,1:19:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各吃各的  太理想了\N{\fs10}Everyone minds his business. It's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.76,1:19:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彼得  那儿有个旧式马桶\N{\fs10}Pete, they got an old-fashioned toilet-
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.73,1:19:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道就是水箱有吊链的那种\N{\fs10}You know, the box and the chain thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.64,1:19:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们或许可把枪用胶带绑在那\N{\fs10}We might be able to tape the gun behind it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.74,1:19:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  麦克  你去餐厅\N{\fs10}All right. Mike, you go to the restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:58.04,1:20:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一面吃一面聊  别紧张\N{\fs10}You eat, you talk for a while, you relax.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.41,1:20:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也可以使对方轻松下来\N{\fs10}You make them relax.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.05,1:20:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后你站起来去上厕所\N{\fs10}Then you get up and go take a leak.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.48,1:20:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得先征求对方同意再去\N{\fs10}No, better still, you ask for permission to go.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.39,1:20:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回来时就开枪\N{\fs10}And when you come back, you come out blasting.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.19,1:20:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别失误  对准头颅各开两枪\N{\fs10}And don't take any chances. Two shots in the head apiece.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.22,1:20:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着  我要一个好手去藏枪\N{\fs10}Now, listen. I want somebody good- and I mean very good- to plant that gun.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.36,1:20:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望我弟弟出来时\N{\fs10}I don't want him coming out
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.73,1:20:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手无寸铁\N{\fs10}with just his dick in his hands.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.70,1:20:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,枪会在那的\N{\fs10}The gun will be there.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.30,1:20:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你开车送他  事后再接他回来\N{\fs10}All right, listen. You drive him and you pick him up after the job.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.47,1:20:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  我们动身了\N{\fs10}Come on. Let's move.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.74,1:20:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他告诉过你事成之后立刻丢枪吗？\N{\fs10}Did he tell you to drop the gun right away?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.91,1:20:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几百万次了\N{\fs10}Yeah, a million times.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.65,1:20:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,切记  朝每人头部开两枪一出厕所后就打\N{\fs10}Don't forget- two shots apiece in the head as soon as you come out the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.37,1:20:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们认为要多久我才能回家？\N{\fs10}How long do you think it'll be before I can come back?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.84,1:20:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少得一年  麦克\N{\fs10}At least a year, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.91,1:21:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会转告妈你临走前不能去看她\N{\fs10}Listen, I'll square with Mom you not seeing her before you leave
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.28,1:21:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会告诉你女朋友的\N{\fs10}I'll get a message to that girlfriend when the time is right.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.02,1:21:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保重\N{\fs10}Take care.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.69,1:21:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保重  麦克\N{\fs10}See you, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.89,1:21:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴你来了  麦克\N{\fs10}I'm glad you came, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.10,1:21:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望我们能把事情谈妥\N{\fs10}I hope we can straighten everything out.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.83,1:22:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事太可怕了  我并不希望发生这种事\N{\fs10}This is terrible. It's not the way I wanted things to go at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.57,1:22:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不该发生这种事的\N{\fs10}It should have never happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.10,1:22:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会在今晚解决一切\N{\fs10}I want to straighten everything out tonight.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.97,1:22:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望我爸烦心\N{\fs10}I don't want my father bothered anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.44,1:22:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会解决的  麦克\N{\fs10}He won't be, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.68,1:22:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以我孩子之名发誓\N{\fs10}I swear on my children he won't be.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.78,1:22:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过谈的时候  你得坦诚才行\N{\fs10}But you got to keep an open mind when we talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.85,1:22:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你不像令兄的坏脾气\N{\fs10}I hope you're not a hothead like your brother Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.32,1:22:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简直没办法和他谈正事\N{\fs10}You can't talk business with him.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.39,1:22:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（意大利文）
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.32,1:22:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是个好孩子\N{\fs10}He's a good kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.13,1:22:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那晚的事我很抱歉  麦克\N{\fs10}I'm sorry about the other night, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.70,1:22:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得搜你的身  转过来\N{\fs10}I gotta frisk you, so turn around, huh?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.23,1:22:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跪在椅子上  脸向我\N{\fs10}On your knees, facing me.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:41.57,1:22:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我干这行已经嫌老了\N{\fs10}I guess I'm getting too old for my job.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.48,1:22:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太多话了\N{\fs10}Too grouchy.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:47.85,1:22:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了别人的激怒  你该明白吧\N{\fs10}Can't stand the aggravation.You know how it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.05,1:22:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没带家伙\N{\fs10}He's clean.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.21,1:23:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到新泽西去？\N{\fs10}We're going to Jersey?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.89,1:23:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许\N{\fs10}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.71,1:23:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,漂亮极了  路\N{\fs10}Nice work, Lou.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:09.09,1:24:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（路易士餐厅）
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.65,1:24:34.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里的意大利菜味道还可以吧？\N{\fs10}How's the Italian food in this restaurant?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.92,1:24:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很棒\N{\fs10}Good.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.12,1:24:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试试这里的小牛肉是本市最棒的\N{\fs10}Try the veal. It's the best in the city.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.26,1:24:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我来一份\N{\fs10}I'll have it.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.23,1:24:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快\N{\fs10}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.16,1:25:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了\N{\fs10}Allright,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.23,1:25:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要和麦克用意大利文交谈\N{\fs10}I'm gonna speak Italian to Mike.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.96,1:25:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请便\N{\fs10}Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.03,1:25:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对现在的形势很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.03,1:25:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你当真这样想?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.45,1:25:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你父亲之间纯粹是生意上的问题
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.17,1:25:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很尊敬你父亲
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.29,1:25:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你父亲的思路已经过时了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.52,1:25:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要知道一件事
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.72,1:25:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是个有荣誉感的人
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.06,1:25:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用再提这些...  我已经知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.39,1:25:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.89,1:26:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经向塔塔利亚家族求援了
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.94,1:26:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前我确信我们将能够达成一个协议
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.96,1:26:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要和平
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.61,1:26:27.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我们把所有的仇恨和不快抛到脑后吧
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.43,1:26:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你玩得...  这样如何
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.24,1:26:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想说的是\N{\fs10}{\fs10}What I want
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.94,1:26:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对我而言  最重要的是\N{\fs10}what's most important to me,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.78,1:26:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保证家父的性命安全\N{\fs10}is that I have a guarantee:No more attempts on my father's life.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.26,1:26:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要我怎么保证？麦克\N{\fs10}What guarantees could I give you?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:53.29,1:26:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是惊弓之鸟\N{\fs10}I am the hunted one.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.99,1:26:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也失手\N{\fs10}I missed my chance.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.69,1:26:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太看重我了  孩子\N{\fs10}You think too much of me, kid.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.30,1:26:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有那么精明\N{\fs10}I'm not that clever.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.97,1:27:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的只是息战而已\N{\fs10}All I want is a truce.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.71,1:27:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须要上厕所  可以吗？\N{\fs10}I have to go to the bathroom. Is that all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.05,1:27:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想去就去吧\N{\fs10}You gotta go, you gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.96,1:27:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我搜过了  他没带家伙\N{\fs10}I frisked him. He's clean.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.79,1:27:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别去太久\N{\fs10}Don't take too long.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.43,1:27:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我搜过好几千人了\N{\fs10}I've frisked a thousand young punks.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.02,1:28:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好些了吧?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.77,1:28:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.90,1:28:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克  你知道吗  你是个意大利人  就像你父亲
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.13,1:29:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲已经病了
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.25,1:29:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等他好些了  我们开个会
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.92,1:29:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要收拾局面
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.96,1:29:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得结束这样的敌对局面
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.05,1:30:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（警方追捕警察杀手）
Dialogue: 0,1:30:05.42,1:30:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（本市黑道瓦解）
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.43,1:30:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（警察队长与毒贩勾结）
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.22,1:30:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（黑社会头子巴西尼接受警方盘问）
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.68,1:31:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（黑社会大火拚）
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.29,1:31:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（黑社会大亨维多柯里昂返家）
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.59,1:32:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  转进来\N{\fs10}Hey, come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.76,1:32:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  你接手\N{\fs10}Joe, you take over.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.94,1:32:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你  爷爷\N{\fs10}I love you, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.78,1:32:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  爸  他还不认识你\N{\fs10}I'm sorry, Pa. He doesn't know you yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.65,1:32:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小家伙  念给爷爷听\N{\fs10}Here you are, big guy. Give it to Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.52,1:32:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  我祝你早日康复  爷爷我希望能快点见到你\N{\fs10}''I hope you get well, Grandpa and I wish I would see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.92,1:33:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱你的孙子  法兰克\N{\fs10}Love, your grandson, Frank.''
Dialogue: 0,1:33:02.19,1:33:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多乖巧
Dialogue: 0,1:33:04.16,1:33:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  到外面去\N{\fs10}Go with your mother.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:06.40,1:33:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把他们带到楼下去吧\N{\fs10}Go ahead. Take 'em downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:11.57,1:33:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.87,1:33:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  卡洛  你也是\N{\fs10}Go on, Carlo. You too.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:18.61,1:33:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧\N{\fs10}Go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.78,1:33:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要烤鸡吗？那是他最喜欢的\N{\fs10}I got chicken cacciatore for you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.08,1:33:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  但他能吃多少呢？\N{\fs10}But how much can you eat?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:40.87,1:33:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？卡洛\N{\fs10}What's the matter with you, Carlo?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:42.90,1:33:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴  去摆桌子吧\N{\fs10}Shut up and set the table.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.35,1:34:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自从麦克劳斯基被杀后\N{\fs10}Since McCluskey's killing
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.09,1:34:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警方瓦解了我们多数业务\N{\fs10}the police have been cracking down on most of our operations.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.19,1:34:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他的家族也是一样\N{\fs10}And also the other families'.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.56,1:34:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牺牲很多\N{\fs10}Been a lot of bad blood.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.26,1:34:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们攻击我们\N{\fs10}They hit us,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:15.80,1:34:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们反击\N{\fs10}so we hit them back.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:17.54,1:34:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,透过我们报社中的连系  我们提供了不少内幕\N{\fs10}Through our contacts in the newspapers we've been able to put out a lot of material
Dialogue: 0,1:34:22.04,1:34:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很多麦克劳斯基跟毒贩索拉索勾结的事\N{\fs10}about McCluskey being linked with Sollozzo in the drug rackets.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.41,1:34:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以风声已经没有那么紧了\N{\fs10}See, things are starting to loosen up.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.88,1:34:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有我派弗雷多去拉斯维加斯\N{\fs10}Dad, I'm sending Fredo to Las Vegas
Dialogue: 0,1:34:34.72,1:34:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在洛杉矶的法兰西斯科阁下会给予他保护\N{\fs10}under the protection of Don Francesco of L.A.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.52,1:34:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我要他休息一会儿  - 我要去学赌场的事\N{\fs10}I want him to rest. I'm going to learn the casino business.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:50.40,1:34:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克在哪？\N{\fs10}Where is Michael?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:04.32,1:35:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀索拉索的是麦克\N{\fs10}It was Michael who killed Sollozzo.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:09.25,1:35:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过他很安全  别担心\N{\fs10}But he's safe. We're starting to work
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.66,1:35:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会把他弄回来的\N{\fs10}to bring him back now.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:34.61,1:35:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你查出塔塔基利亚躲在哪儿没？\N{\fs10}I want you to find out where that little pimp Tattaglia is hiding.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.71,1:35:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要他的命  现在\N{\fs10}I want his ass now- right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.05,1:35:40.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 听我说  山尼  - 什么事？\N{\fs10}- Hey, Sonny. - What?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.75,1:35:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在局势才刚刚缓和下来\N{\fs10}Things are starting to loosen up a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:42.59,1:35:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你若去追塔塔基利亚\N{\fs10}If you go after Tattaglia,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.16,1:35:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又会引起一场大战的\N{\fs10}all hell's going to break loose.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:45.39,1:35:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等事情平静一点让爸爸去协调\N{\fs10}Let the smoke clear. Pop can negotiate.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.19,1:35:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  爸爸在身体好转之前什么都不能做\N{\fs10}No, Pop can't do nothing till he's better.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.83,1:35:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要决定什么对我们最有利\N{\fs10}I'm gonna decide-
Dialogue: 0,1:35:49.96,1:35:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  可是你那场火拚使我们损失很多\N{\fs10}All right, but your war's costing us a lot of money.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:51.76,1:35:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有任何进帐  我们不能做事\N{\fs10}Nothing's coming in. We can't do business.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:53.46,1:35:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们也不行  别担心\N{\fs10}Neither can they. Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.60,1:35:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 他们没有我们损失那么大  - 请你别担心这点\N{\fs10}- We can't afford a stalemate. - No more stalemate.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.47,1:36:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会以宰了那老混蛋来做结束\N{\fs10}I'm gonna end it by killing that old bastard.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:00.27,1:36:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是  你现在名声很大你一定很得意吧\N{\fs10}You're getting a great reputation. I hope you're enjoying it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.74,1:36:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,依照我叫你做的去做\N{\fs10}Do what I tell you to do!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.34,1:36:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死的  我若有个西西里人来当我的战略军师\N{\fs10}Goddamn it, if I had a wartime consigliere- a Sicilian-
Dialogue: 0,1:36:06.41,1:36:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就不会落到这种地步了\N{\fs10}I wouldn't be in this shape!
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.35,1:36:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸有杰安可  看看我有什么？\N{\fs10}Pop had Genco. Look what I got.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.52,1:36:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我不是有意的\N{\fs10}I'm sorry. I didn't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:18.09,1:36:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈煮了晚餐  今天是星期天\N{\fs10}Mom made a little dinner. It's Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.86,1:36:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑人对我们哈林区的银行新政策非常满意\N{\fs10}Niggers are having a good time with our policy banks up there in Harlem.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:26.43,1:36:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开着新凯迪拉克我先帮他们付一半的钱\N{\fs10}Driving them new Cadillacs, paying 50? on a bet.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.57,1:36:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从他们开始赚钱时我就知道这会发生\N{\fs10}I knew that was gonna happen as soon as they started making big money.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:33.80,1:36:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸从来不在餐桌上当着孩子们谈他的公事\N{\fs10}Papa never talked business at the table in front of the kids.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:37.34,1:36:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 闭嘴  康妮 - 不准你叫她闭嘴  知道吗？\N{\fs10}- Shut up, Connie. - Don't you ever tell her to shut up. You got that?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:41.85,1:36:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别干预\N{\fs10}Santino, don't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:45.48,1:36:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山尼 汤姆吃过饭后  我想与你们谈谈\N{\fs10}Sonny, Tom, I'd like to talk to you, maybe after dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.22,1:36:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我对家族也许能帮很多的  - 我们不在餐桌上讨论公事\N{\fs10}I could be doing more for the family. We don't discuss business at the table.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.40,1:37:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向你致敬  汤马西诺阁下\N{\fs10}I kiss your hand, Don Tommasino.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.48,1:37:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克\N{\fs10}Mike
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.88,1:37:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为何离房子那么远？\N{\fs10}I kiss your hand, Don Tommasino.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:50.51,1:37:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可知万一你出了事  我要向令尊负责的\N{\fs10}You know I'm responsible to your father for your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:53.15,1:37:54.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保镖们都在这\N{\fs10}The bodyguards are here.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.19,1:37:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是十分危险\N{\fs10}It's still dangerous...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.59,1:38:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听纽约的山提诺说的\N{\fs10}We've heard from Santino in New York...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:01.16,1:38:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的敌人知道你在这了\N{\fs10}Your enemies know you're here.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.20,1:38:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山提诺有没有说我何时能回去？\N{\fs10}Did Santino say when I can go back?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.60,1:38:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不行\N{\fs10}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.37,1:38:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前是不可能的\N{\fs10}It's out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.64,1:38:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fs10}Thanks
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.24,1:38:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在要去哪里？\N{\fs10}Where are you going now?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.88,1:38:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯里昂村
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.48,1:38:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐我的车去\N{\fs10}Take my car.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.05,1:38:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想走路\N{\fs10}I want to walk.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.55,1:38:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心点\N{\fs10}Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.41,1:38:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克  柯里昂村到了
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.52,1:39:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的男人都到哪去了？\N{\fs10}Where have all the men gone?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.29,1:39:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们全都在战争中死了\N{\fs10}They're all dead from vendettas.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:09.36,1:39:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里是死者的姓名\N{\fs10}There are the names of the dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.38,1:40:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的老天  好一个美女\N{\fs10}Mamma mia what a beauty.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:11.56,1:40:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像中邪了一样\N{\fs10}I think you got hit by the thunderbolt.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:19.03,1:40:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克\N{\fs10}Mike
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.53,1:40:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在西西里  女人比猎枪还危险\N{\fs10}In Sicily women are more dangerous than shotguns.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:47.46,1:40:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打猎有收获吗？\N{\fs10}Did you have a good hunt?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:49.66,1:40:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认识这一带所有的女孩吗？\N{\fs10}You know all the girls around here?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.03,1:40:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们看到几位真正的美人\N{\fs10}We saw some real beauties.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:01.74,1:41:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中一位让我们的朋友触电了\N{\fs10}One of them struck our friend like a thunderbolt.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.88,1:41:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她可真够骚了\N{\fs10}She would tempt the devil himself.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.35,1:41:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她全身上下都很美\N{\fs10}Really put together.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.16,1:41:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么漂亮的头发  嘴\N{\fs10}Such hair, such mouth!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:23.29,1:41:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一带的女孩都很美而且很贞洁\N{\fs10}The girls around here are beautiful... but virtuous.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.03,1:41:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个穿着紫色衣服\N{\fs10}This one had a purple dress...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.77,1:41:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,头发上绑着紫色的缎带\N{\fs10}And a purple ribbon in her hair.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.64,1:41:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来像希腊人而非意大利人\N{\fs10}A type more Greek than Italian.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.64,1:41:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认识她吗？\N{\fs10}Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:42.15,1:41:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不认识\N{\fs10}No
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.58,1:41:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在本镇没有那样子的女孩\N{\fs10}There's no girl like that in this town.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.02,1:41:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天  我明白了\N{\fs10}My God, I understand!
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.83,1:41:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不对了？\N{\fs10}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.63,1:42:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走\N{\fs10}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.53,1:42:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他女儿\N{\fs10}It's his daughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:03.87,1:42:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫他出来\N{\fs10}Tell him to come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:30.26,1:42:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法布利奇欧  你翻译\N{\fs10}Fabrizio, you translate.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.93,1:42:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  先生\N{\fs10}Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.57,1:42:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我若冒犯了你  我道歉\N{\fs10}I apologize if I offended you.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:39.70,1:42:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我初到贵地\N{\fs10}I'm a stranger in this country
Dialogue: 0,1:42:42.77,1:42:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我无意冒犯你和令嫒\N{\fs10}and I meant no disrespect to you or your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:51.52,1:42:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是个美国人到西西里来避风头\N{\fs10}I'm an American hiding in Sicily.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:55.85,1:42:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是麦克柯里昂\N{\fs10}My name is Michael Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.16,1:43:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人会为了钱而出卖我在此的消息\N{\fs10}There are people who would pay a lot of money for that information.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:06.40,1:43:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但那样令嫒会失去父亲\N{\fs10}But then your daughter would lose a father
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.97,1:43:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而不是得到一位丈夫\N{\fs10}instead of gaining a husband.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:21.51,1:43:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想认识你女儿\N{\fs10}I want to meet your daughter
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.21,1:43:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但要在你的同意下\N{\fs10}with your permission
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.45,1:43:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,及在你的家人的监督之下\N{\fs10}and under the supervision of your family
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.92,1:43:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对是诚心诚意\N{\fs10}with all respect.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.59,1:43:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星期天早上到我家来  我叫维提\N{\fs10}Come to my house Sunday morning. My name is Vitelli.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:46.17,1:43:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.94,1:43:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她叫什么名字？\N{\fs10}What's her name?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:49.97,1:43:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾波洛妮亚
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.71,1:43:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很美的名字
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.16,1:44:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是小女艾波洛妮亚
Dialogue: 0,1:44:48.80,1:44:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位是麦克柯里昂先生
Dialogue: 0,1:45:09.22,1:45:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,1:46:43.11,1:46:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我回来干你\N{\fs10}I'll knock you dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:51.76,1:46:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,废话少说\N{\fs10}Save it for the library.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:57.59,1:46:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  我们得去接我妹妹\N{\fs10}Come on. We've got to pick up my sister.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:18.25,1:47:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？\N{\fs10}What's matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:22.45,1:47:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？\N{\fs10}What's matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:26.02,1:47:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 是我的错  - 他在哪？\N{\fs10}- It was my fault! - Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.52,1:47:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山尼  拜托  是我的错\N{\fs10}Sonny, please. It was my fault. I hit him.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:29.43,1:47:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山尼  是我的错  是我先开始打他的\N{\fs10}I started a fight with him. Please, Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:31.86,1:47:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求你  山尼  我先打他的\N{\fs10}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:35.00,1:47:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我...   - 好了
Dialogue: 0,1:47:39.67,1:47:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是叫医生来看你  好吗？\N{\fs10}I'm just gonna get a doctor to come and take a look at you.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:43.57,1:47:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山尼  求你别动手\N{\fs10}Sonny, please don't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:48.18,1:47:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  你是怎么了？我会怎么做？\N{\fs10}What's the matter with you? What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:50.31,1:47:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你肚里的孩子做遗腹子吗？\N{\fs10}Am I gonna make that baby an orphan before he's born?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:56.52,1:47:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了吗？\N{\fs10}All right?
Dialogue: 0,1:47:57.79,1:48:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙把洋基队打得惨兮兮\N{\fs10}Still betting the Yankees pretty heavy?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:01.02,1:48:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫他们不要再接受投注了\N{\fs10}Tell him to stop taking action, all right?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:04.49,1:48:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们上周末输的钱够多了\N{\fs10}You lost enough money last weekend to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.64,1:48:15.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛  到这来...\N{\fs10}Carlo, come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:12.36,1:49:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你再碰我妹妹一下我会杀了你\N{\fs10}You touch my sister again, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:49:31.18,1:49:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（意大利文）
Dialogue: 0,1:53:08.90,1:53:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你会来  凯怎么不先打个电话来\N{\fs10}Weren't expecting you. You should call.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:13.24,1:53:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有打  我写过信也打过电话\N{\fs10}Yes, well, I have. I've tried writing and calling.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:17.64,1:53:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要和麦克连络\N{\fs10}Now, I wanna reach Michael.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:19.98,1:53:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人知道他在哪\N{\fs10}Nobody knows where he is.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:21.54,1:53:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们知道他没事  但仅此而已\N{\fs10}We know he's all right, but that's all.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:26.72,1:53:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 怎么了？  - 那是件车祸但没有人受伤\N{\fs10}- What was that? - That's an accident. But nobody was hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:31.49,1:53:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆\N{\fs10}Tom.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:32.96,1:53:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请你把这封信交给麦克好吗？\N{\fs10}Would you give this letter to Michael, please?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:37.09,1:53:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我若接受了法院可以证实我晓得他在哪里\N{\fs10}if I accepted that in a court of law they could prove I have knowledge of his whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:42.60,1:53:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有耐心点  凯他会与你连络的  好吗？\N{\fs10}Just be patient. He'll get in touch with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:53:45.07,1:53:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我让我的计程车走了我是否能进去打电话叫一辆？\N{\fs10}I let my cab go. Can I come in to call another one?
Dialogue: 0,1:53:48.97,1:53:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  对不起  来吧\N{\fs10}Come on. I'm sorry. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:11.86,1:54:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛在吗？\N{\fs10}Is Carlo there?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:13.66,1:54:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你是哪位？  - 我是卡洛的朋友\N{\fs10}- Who's this? - This is a friend of Carlo's.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:16.27,1:54:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉他我今晚没空\N{\fs10}Would you tell him that I can't make it tonight until later?
Dialogue: 0,1:54:25.28,1:54:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贱人\N{\fs10}Bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:28.68,1:54:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 晚餐在桌上了  - 我还不饿\N{\fs10}- Dinner's on the table. - I'm not hungry yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:31.31,1:54:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 晚餐在桌上快凉了  - 我有约了\N{\fs10}Your food is on the table. It's getting cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:34.72,1:54:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚叫我给你做晚餐的\N{\fs10}- I'll eat out later. - You told me to make you dinner.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:36.49,1:54:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 滚开好吗？  - 你才滚开\N{\fs10}Hey, vaffancolo, eh? I'll vaffanculo you!
Dialogue: 0,1:54:45.73,1:54:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这个意大利婊子\N{\fs10}This little guinea brat.
Dialogue: 0,1:54:52.57,1:54:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  全都打破了\N{\fs10}That's it. Break it all,
Dialogue: 0,1:54:53.84,1:54:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这被宠坏的女娃  全打破了\N{\fs10}you spoiled guinea brat. Break it all!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:06.12,1:55:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为何不把那个妓女带回家吃晚饭？\N{\fs10}Why don't you bring your whore home for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:10.45,1:55:11.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许我会  有何不可？\N{\fs10}Maybe I will. Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:55:18.46,1:55:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在把它清干净\N{\fs10}Now clean it up!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:19.83,1:55:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要  我才不要\N{\fs10}Like hell I will!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:22.17,1:55:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清干净  贱人\N{\fs10}Clean it up, you guinea spoiled brat!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:24.63,1:55:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清干净  我说清干净\N{\fs10}Clean it up! I said clean it up!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:30.84,1:55:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清干净\N{\fs10}Clean it up!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:33.48,1:55:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fs10}No.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:35.15,1:55:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清干净  他妈的\N{\fs10}You son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:37.78,1:55:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清干净...\N{\fs10}Clean it up!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:40.42,1:55:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清干净\N{\fs10}Clean it up!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:42.52,1:55:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来  杀我  像你爸一样当凶手\N{\fs10}Come on, now! Kill me! Be a murderer like your father!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:45.35,1:55:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  你们姓柯里昂的全是凶手\N{\fs10}- All you Corleones are murderers! - I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:47.32,1:55:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  贱人\N{\fs10}- Come on! - I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:49.49,1:55:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  杀我  滚\N{\fs10}Kill me! Get up! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:55:53.60,1:55:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我恨你  - 快点  否则我要杀你了\N{\fs10}- I hate you! - Now I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:57.33,1:55:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这意大利贱货\N{\fs10}You guinea brat, you.
Dialogue: 0,1:55:59.16,1:56:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滚出来\N{\fs10}Get out here!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:01.02,1:56:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fs10}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:02.81,1:56:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fs10}No!
Dialogue: 0,1:56:10.06,1:56:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,康妮  怎么回事？\N{\fs10}Connie, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:11.70,1:56:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听不见你说的  什么事？\N{\fs10}I can't hear you. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:14.27,1:56:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,康妮  说大声点  孩子在哭\N{\fs10}Talk louder. The baby's crying.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:17.35,1:56:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山提诺  我听不懂  我不明白\N{\fs10}Santino, I can't understand- I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:21.51,1:56:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？康妮？\N{\fs10}Yeah, Connie.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:28.38,1:56:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听我说  你在那等着\N{\fs10}Listen, you wait there.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:32.72,1:56:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  你在那等着就对了\N{\fs10}No, you just wait there.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:37.37,1:56:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王八蛋\N{\fs10}That son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:41.28,1:56:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 怎么回事？  - 王八蛋\N{\fs10}Sonny, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,1:56:46.92,1:56:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快开门  站起来\N{\fs10}Open the goddamn gate. Get off your ass.
Dialogue: 0,1:56:58.07,1:56:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,山尼\N{\fs10}Sonny
Dialogue: 0,1:57:05.00,1:57:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 山尼  - 滚开\N{\fs10}- Sonny, come on! - Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:57:08.74,1:57:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟他一起去  快点\N{\fs10}Go after him. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,1:57:40.24,1:57:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王八蛋  快点...\N{\fs10}Son of a bitch. Come on! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:59:31.05,1:59:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把那个给我\N{\fs10}Give me a drop.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:41.32,1:59:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太太在楼上哭\N{\fs10}My wife is crying upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:46.00,1:59:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听见车子到家里来\N{\fs10}I hear cars coming to the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:53.14,1:59:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的好军师\N{\fs10}Consigliere of mine
Dialogue: 0,1:59:56.44,1:59:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都知道  只有我毫不知情\N{\fs10}I think you should tell your Don what everyone seems to know.
Dialogue: 0,1:59:59.94,2:00:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没告诉妈任何事\N{\fs10}I didn't tell Mama anything.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:03.21,2:00:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正预备去叫醒你  并告诉你\N{\fs10}I was about to come up and wake you just now and tell you.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:09.85,2:00:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你需要先喝杯酒\N{\fs10}But you needed a drink first.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:18.86,2:00:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你喝过酒了\N{\fs10}Now you've had your drink.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:26.90,2:00:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在收费站杀了山尼\N{\fs10}They shot Sonny on the causeway.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:30.11,2:00:31.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他死了\N{\fs10}He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:48.39,2:00:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要追查此事\N{\fs10}I want no inquiries made.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:55.06,2:00:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要复仇\N{\fs10}I want no acts of vengeance.
Dialogue: 0,2:00:59.14,2:01:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你安排一次会议\N{\fs10}I want you to arrange a meeting
Dialogue: 0,2:01:02.91,2:01:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与五大家族的族长\N{\fs10}with the heads of the five families.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:07.71,2:01:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这场火拚该终止了\N{\fs10}This war stops now.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:31.93,2:01:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打电话给包纳萨拉\N{\fs10}Call Bonasera.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.20,2:01:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在需要他了\N{\fs10}We need him now.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:48.72,2:01:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是汤姆哈金\N{\fs10}This is Tom Hagen calling for Vito Corleone
Dialogue: 0,2:01:50.15,2:01:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,维多柯里昂要我打这个电话\N{\fs10}at his request.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:53.82,2:01:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你欠教父一次人情\N{\fs10}Now, you owe your Don a service.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:56.43,2:01:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他相信你会回报他的\N{\fs10}he has no doubt that you will repay it.
Dialogue: 0,2:01:59.96,2:02:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他在一小时后会到你的殡仪馆去\N{\fs10}Now, he will be at your funeral parlor in one hour.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:02.63,2:02:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请在那等待\N{\fs10}Be there to greet him.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:25.66,2:02:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友\N{\fs10}Well, my friend
Dialogue: 0,2:02:27.96,2:02:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你预备为我服务了吗？\N{\fs10}are you ready to do me this service?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:30.43,2:02:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  但你要我怎么做？\N{\fs10}Yes. What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,2:02:41.84,2:02:47.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你尽你一切的力量和技巧好好为他化妆\N{\fs10}I want you to use all your powers and all your skills.
Dialogue: 0,2:02:50.58,2:02:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要他母亲看到他这个样子\N{\fs10}I don't want his mother to see him this way.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:09.70,2:03:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看他们是怎么对我的孩子？\N{\fs10}Look how they massacred my boy.
Dialogue: 0,2:03:42.93,2:03:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教你英语会安全一点\N{\fs10}It's safer to teach you English!
Dialogue: 0,2:03:45.24,2:03:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会英语\N{\fs10}I know English...
Dialogue: 0,2:03:46.77,2:03:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星期一 星期二 星期四 星期三 星期五 星期日 星期六\N{\fs10}Monday, Tuesday, Thursday, Wednesday, Friday, Sunday, Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:07.62,2:04:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好  汤马西诺阁下\N{\fs10}Greetings, Don Tommasino.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:09.96,2:04:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克在教我开车\N{\fs10}Michael is teaching me to drive...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:13.86,2:04:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我开给你看\N{\fs10}watch, I'll show you.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:16.37,2:04:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家里的一切都还好吧？\N{\fs10}How are things in Palermo?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:19.07,2:04:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,年轻人不再尊重任何事了\N{\fs10}Young people don't respect anything any more...
Dialogue: 0,2:04:22.20,2:04:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时代越变越糟\N{\fs10}times are changing for the worse.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:27.04,2:04:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这地方对你已变得太危险了\N{\fs10}This place has become too dangerous for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:34.58,2:04:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你搬到西拉古莎附近的别墅\N{\fs10}I want you to move to a villa near Siracusa... right now.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:45.29,2:04:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不对了？\N{\fs10}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,2:04:48.03,2:04:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由美国传来的坏消息\N{\fs10}Bad news from America.
Dialogue: 0,2:04:51.83,2:04:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥山尼  他们杀了他\N{\fs10}Your brother, Santino, they killed him.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:01.78,2:05:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们走了  你答应的\N{\fs10}Let's go... you promised.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:24.00,2:05:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 法布利奇欧  - 什么事？\N{\fs10}- Fabrizio. - Yes, sir?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:25.57,2:05:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,备车\N{\fs10}Get the car.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:27.44,2:05:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要自己开吗？老板\N{\fs10}Are you driving yourself, boss?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:29.24,2:05:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fs10}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:30.24,2:05:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太太跟你一起去吗？\N{\fs10}Is your wife coming with you?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:31.84,2:05:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我要你送她回娘家  等一切安全点再说\N{\fs10}Take her to her father's house till I know things are safe.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:35.48,2:05:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的  随你吩咐  老板\N{\fs10}Anything you say, boss.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:43.72,2:05:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡罗  艾波洛妮亚呢？\N{\fs10}Calo, where is Apollonia?
Dialogue: 0,2:05:46.32,2:05:50.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她想给你个惊喜  她要开车\N{\fs10}She' going to surprise you. She wants to drive.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:52.09,2:05:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她会当个好的美国太太\N{\fs10}She'll make a good Amrican wife.
Dialogue: 0,2:05:55.70,2:05:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  我去拿行李\N{\fs10}Wait, I'll get the baggage.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:08.04,2:06:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法布利奇欧\N{\fs10}Fabrizio!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:10.51,2:06:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪？\N{\fs10}Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,2:06:13.05,2:06:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克  在那等  我开过去\N{\fs10}Michael. Wait there! I'll drive to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:22.12,2:06:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  艾波洛妮亚...\N{\fs10}No, Apollonia!
Dialogue: 0,2:06:46.72,2:06:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴西尼阁下\N{\fs10}Don Barzini, I want to thank you
Dialogue: 0,2:06:47.92,2:06:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你帮我安排这次会议\N{\fs10}for helping me organize this meeting here today.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:52.76,2:06:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有纽约和新泽西其他五大家族的族长\N{\fs10}And also the other heads of the five families from New York and New Jersey.
Dialogue: 0,2:06:59.36,2:07:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布朗区的卡麦克里安诺\N{\fs10}Carmine Cuneo from the Bronx.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:02.53,2:07:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及... 布鲁克林的\N{\fs10}From Brooklyn
Dialogue: 0,2:07:07.60,2:07:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲立浦塔塔基利亚\N{\fs10}Philip Tattaglia.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:11.24,2:07:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由史坦登岛来的\N{\fs10}And from Staten Island
Dialogue: 0,2:07:14.31,2:07:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,维多史特基\N{\fs10}we have with us Victor Strachi.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:17.68,2:07:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,及由加州堪萨斯来的同道\N{\fs10}And all the other associates that came as far as from California and Kansas City
Dialogue: 0,2:07:23.45,2:07:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及全国其他各地区所来的朋友\N{\fs10}and all the other territories of the country.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:26.19,2:07:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们\N{\fs10}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:34.16,2:07:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情怎么会演变成如此？\N{\fs10}How did things ever get so far?
Dialogue: 0,2:07:37.63,2:07:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不晓得\N{\fs10}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:41.27,2:07:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那么的不幸及那么的没必要\N{\fs10}It was so unfortunate and so unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:47.91,2:07:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔塔基利亚失去了一个儿子\N{\fs10}Tattaglia lost a son
Dialogue: 0,2:07:50.21,2:07:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是\N{\fs10}and I lost a son.
Dialogue: 0,2:07:53.72,2:07:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们该停手了\N{\fs10}We're quits,
Dialogue: 0,2:07:54.98,2:07:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是塔塔基利亚同意\N{\fs10}and if Tattaglia agrees
Dialogue: 0,2:07:57.29,2:08:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意让事情恢复以前的局面\N{\fs10}then I'm willing to let things go on the way they were before.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:02.79,2:08:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都很感谢柯里昂阁下召开这次会议\N{\fs10}We are all grateful to Don Corleone for calling this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:06.43,2:08:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们都了解他是个有信用的人\N{\fs10}We all know him as a man of his word.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:09.27,2:08:11.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他为人谦虚  总是能讲道理\N{\fs10}A modest man. He'll always listen to reason.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:11.90,2:08:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  巴西尼阁下\N{\fs10}Yes, Don Barzini.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:14.07,2:08:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他太谦虚了\N{\fs10}He's too modest.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:16.04,2:08:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有的法官与政客没有不听他指示的\N{\fs10}He had all the judges and politicians in his pocket.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:20.44,2:08:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他却拒绝与我们分享\N{\fs10}He refused to share them.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:23.35,2:08:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我何时拒绝过与大家分享？\N{\fs10}When did I ever refuse an accommodation?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:27.22,2:08:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在座的全都认识我\N{\fs10}All of you know me here.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:30.62,2:08:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了一次以外  我何时拒绝过？\N{\fs10}When did I ever refuse, except one time?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:34.79,2:08:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们知道为什么\N{\fs10}And why?
Dialogue: 0,2:08:37.36,2:08:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我相信毒品生意在往后几年会毁了我们\N{\fs10}Because I believe this drug business is gonna destroy us in the years to come.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:43.30,2:08:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不像赌 酒和女人\N{\fs10}I mean, it's not like gambling or liquor or even women
Dialogue: 0,2:08:47.67,2:08:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些是人们想要的东西只是教会不准我们做而已\N{\fs10}which is something that most people want nowadays and is forbidden to them by the pezzonovante of the church.
Dialogue: 0,2:08:53.58,2:08:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使警察过去在赌博等方面愿意协助我们\N{\fs10}Even the police departments that have helped us in the past with gambling and other things
Dialogue: 0,2:08:58.38,2:09:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但一提到毒品他们会拒绝帮忙\N{\fs10}are gonna refuse to help us when it comes to narcotics.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:02.89,2:09:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以前那么想现在想法依然不变\N{\fs10}And I believed that then and I believe that now.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:08.06,2:09:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时代变了\N{\fs10}Times have changed.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:10.29,2:09:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不像昔日了\N{\fs10}It's not like the old days
Dialogue: 0,2:09:12.56,2:09:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们能做任何我们想做的事\N{\fs10}when we could do anything we want.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:15.13,2:09:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你拒绝合作实在不够朋友\N{\fs10}A refusal is not the act of a friend.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:18.07,2:09:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯里昂阁下握有全纽约法律界以及政客的势力\N{\fs10}If Don Corleone had all the judges and politicians in New York
Dialogue: 0,2:09:22.14,2:09:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就必须与大家分享\N{\fs10}then he must share them
Dialogue: 0,2:09:23.77,2:09:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让大家都能利用他们\N{\fs10}or let others use them.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:25.21,2:09:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他必须让我们分汲利益大家一起发财\N{\fs10}He must let us draw the water from the well.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:29.24,2:09:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然他能因这种服务而向大家收费\N{\fs10}Certainly, he can present a bill for such services.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:32.95,2:09:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟我们不是共产党\N{\fs10}After all, we are not Communists.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:38.72,2:09:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我同样的也不相信毒品\N{\fs10}I also don't believe in drugs.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:41.86,2:09:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多年来我付手下优厚的待遇\N{\fs10}For years, I paid my people extra
Dialogue: 0,2:09:44.33,2:09:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使他们不去沾毒品\N{\fs10}so they wouldn't do that kind of business.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:46.86,2:09:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,避免有人来找他们并且说我有白粉\N{\fs10}Somebody comes to them and says, ''I have powders.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:49.90,2:09:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你只要投资三千元到四千元\N{\fs10}If you put up a three, four-thousand-dollar investment
Dialogue: 0,2:09:53.74,2:09:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以赚到五万元\N{\fs10}we can make 50,000 distributing.''
Dialogue: 0,2:09:57.47,2:09:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们怎能抗拒得了\N{\fs10}So they can't resist.
Dialogue: 0,2:09:59.14,2:10:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想以正派的方法来经营毒品生意\N{\fs10}I want to control it as a business to keep it respectable.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:03.91,2:10:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要它们接近学校\N{\fs10}I don't want it near schools.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:05.61,2:10:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要把它们卖给孩子\N{\fs10}I don't want it sold to children.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:08.58,2:10:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是残害幼苗\N{\fs10}That's an infamia.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:11.62,2:10:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想卖给那些黑人或是在有色人种中流通\N{\fs10}In my city, we'll keep the traffic in the dark people, the colored.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:15.62,2:10:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们反正是动物  所以让他们去坠落吧\N{\fs10}They're animals anyway, so let them lose their souls.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:25.43,2:10:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我本希望能合理的讨论一些事\N{\fs10}I hoped that we could come here and reason together.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:30.44,2:10:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身为一个讲道理的人\N{\fs10}As a reasonable man,
Dialogue: 0,2:10:31.97,2:10:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意为此事找个和平解决之道\N{\fs10}I'm willing to do whatever's necessary to find a peaceful solution to these problems.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:37.65,2:10:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们全都达成协议\N{\fs10}Then we are agreed.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:39.11,2:10:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毒品生意可以做但要有限制\N{\fs10}The traffic in drugs will be permitted but controlled.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:42.15,2:10:44.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯里昂阁下会给我们东部的保护\N{\fs10}Don Corleone will give us protection in the east
Dialogue: 0,2:10:45.15,2:10:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我们和平相处\N{\fs10}and there will be the peace.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:46.82,2:10:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我必须有柯里昂阁下的确切保证\N{\fs10}But I must have strict assurance from Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:50.56,2:10:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万一他的地位越来越坚固之后\N{\fs10}As time goes by and his position becomes stronger
Dialogue: 0,2:10:53.90,2:10:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是否会采取复仇行动\N{\fs10}will he attempt any individual vendetta?
Dialogue: 0,2:10:56.43,2:10:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着我们这全是讲理的人\N{\fs10}Look, we are all reasonable men here.
Dialogue: 0,2:10:58.60,2:11:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不需像是律师般给什么确切保证\N{\fs10}We don't have to give assurances as if we were lawyers.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:02.04,2:11:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你谈到复仇\N{\fs10}You talk about vengeance.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:04.81,2:11:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,复仇会让你的儿子复活吗？\N{\fs10}Is vengeance gonna bring your son back to you?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:08.14,2:11:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者我的儿子？\N{\fs10}Or my boy to me?
Dialogue: 0,2:11:10.75,2:11:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再去计较我儿子的死\N{\fs10}I forego the vengeance of my son.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:16.39,2:11:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我有个自私的要求\N{\fs10}But I have selfish reasons.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:20.96,2:11:25.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的小儿子被迫离开这个国家\N{\fs10}My youngest son was forced to leave this country
Dialogue: 0,2:11:26.53,2:11:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都因为这索拉索的事\N{\fs10}because of this Sollozzo business.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:29.50,2:11:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须安排让他安全的回来\N{\fs10}All right. And I have to make arrangements to bring him back here safely,
Dialogue: 0,2:11:34.50,2:11:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗脱种种无中生有的罪名\N{\fs10}cleared of all these false charges.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:38.61,2:11:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我是个迷信的人\N{\fs10}But I'm a superstitious man.
Dialogue: 0,2:11:41.88,2:11:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若是他不幸发生意外\N{\fs10}And if some unlucky accident should
Dialogue: 0,2:11:43.75,2:11:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或被警察开枪打死\N{\fs10}befall him if he should get shot in the head by a police officer
Dialogue: 0,2:11:48.58,2:11:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或在牢里上吊\N{\fs10}or if he should hang himself in his jail cell
Dialogue: 0,2:11:52.25,2:11:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是他被闪电击中\N{\fs10}of if he's struck by a bolt of lightening-
Dialogue: 0,2:11:56.39,2:11:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我会怪罪于在这房间内的诸位\N{\fs10}then I'm going to blame some of the people in this room.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:01.60,2:12:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到那时候我就不会再客气了\N{\fs10}And that I do not forgive.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:06.44,2:12:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但除了那个以外\N{\fs10}But that aside
Dialogue: 0,2:12:11.87,2:12:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以我孙子的性命发誓\N{\fs10}let me say that I swear on the souls of my grandchildren
Dialogue: 0,2:12:19.15,2:12:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会是打破我们今天和议的人\N{\fs10}that I will not be the one to break the peace we've made here today.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:48.94,2:12:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当我见塔塔基利亚的人时\N{\fs10}When I meet with the Tattaglia people,
Dialogue: 0,2:12:50.88,2:12:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应否坚持那些毒品中间人都没有前科？\N{\fs10}should I insist that all these drug middlemen have clean records?
Dialogue: 0,2:12:54.52,2:12:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,提出来无妨  不要坚持\N{\fs10}Mention it. Don't insist.
Dialogue: 0,2:12:58.69,2:13:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴西尼这种人你不说他也明白\N{\fs10}Barzini is a man who'll know that without being told.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:02.59,2:13:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说塔塔基利亚\N{\fs10}You mean Tattaglia.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:05.39,2:13:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔塔基利亚是个下三滥？\N{\fs10}Tattaglia's a pimp.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:08.26,2:13:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他根本没本事干掉山提诺\N{\fs10}He never could've outfought Santino.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:13.97,2:13:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在今天以前并不晓得\N{\fs10}But I didn't know until this day that it was
Dialogue: 0,2:13:17.81,2:13:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直是巴西尼在主使\N{\fs10}Barzini all along.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:34.96,2:13:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  南西\N{\fs10}Come on, Nancy.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:38.16,2:13:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家紧跟在一起  布莱恩\N{\fs10}Keep together, everyone. Brian?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:42.06,2:13:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的...\N{\fs10}All right.
Dialogue: 0,2:13:57.08,2:13:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回来多久了？\N{\fs10}How long have you been back?
Dialogue: 0,2:13:59.78,2:14:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一年了\N{\fs10}I've been back a year.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:03.12,2:14:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许还不止\N{\fs10}Longer than that, I think.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:07.79,2:14:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,见到你真好  凯\N{\fs10}It's good to see you, Kay.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:21.17,2:14:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在为我父亲做事\N{\fs10}I'm working for my father now, Kay.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:26.21,2:14:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他病了  病的很重\N{\fs10}He's been sick.Very sick.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:30.78,2:14:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你不像他  麦克\N{\fs10}But you're not like him.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:32.81,2:14:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以为你不会成为令尊那样的人\N{\fs10}I thought you weren't going to become a man like your father.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:35.45,2:14:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是你所告诉我的\N{\fs10}That's what you told me.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:38.55,2:14:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家父与其他有权的人一样\N{\fs10}My father's no different than any other powerful man.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:42.89,2:14:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是那种要对其他人负责任的人\N{\fs10}Any man who's responsible for other people.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:47.60,2:14:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是参议员或是总统\N{\fs10}Like a senator or a president.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:49.97,2:14:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道你说这些话有多天真\N{\fs10}Do you know how naive you sound?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:51.67,2:14:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？\N{\fs10}Why?
Dialogue: 0,2:14:52.73,2:14:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,参议员及总统不杀人\N{\fs10}Senators and presidents don't have men killed.
Dialogue: 0,2:14:58.67,2:15:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁天真？凯\N{\fs10}Who's being naive, Kay?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:01.91,2:15:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家父做事的那一套已过时了\N{\fs10}Kay, My father's way of doing things is over.It's finished.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:05.31,2:15:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连他都晓得那一点\N{\fs10}Even he knows that.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:07.72,2:15:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说在五年之内\N{\fs10}I mean, in five years
Dialogue: 0,2:15:09.12,2:15:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯里昂家族会完全合法化\N{\fs10}the Corleone family is going to be completely legitimate.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:13.62,2:15:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信我\N{\fs10}Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:14.72,2:15:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚我未来的走向\N{\fs10}That's all I can tell you about my business.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:17.03,2:15:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯\N{\fs10}Kay
Dialogue: 0,2:15:19.29,2:15:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克  你为何到这来？\N{\fs10}Why did you come here?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:21.66,2:15:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？\N{\fs10}Why?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:23.80,2:15:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟想要我怎么样？\N{\fs10}What do you want with me
Dialogue: 0,2:15:25.33,2:15:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么多年来你不打电话也不写信\N{\fs10}after all this time without even calling or writing?
Dialogue: 0,2:15:28.74,2:15:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来这是因为我需要你  我关心你\N{\fs10}I came here because I need you. Because I care for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:32.04,2:15:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再说了  麦克\N{\fs10}- Please stop it, Michael.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:33.38,2:15:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为...\N{\fs10}- Because...
Dialogue: 0,2:15:35.01,2:15:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你嫁给我\N{\fs10}I want you to marry me.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:37.88,2:15:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太迟了\N{\fs10}- It's too late. - Please.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:39.18,2:15:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯\N{\fs10}Kay
Dialogue: 0,2:15:42.05,2:15:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会做任何事以弥补过去所发生的事\N{\fs10}I'll do anything you ask to make up for what's happened to us.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:47.99,2:15:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为那很重要  凯\N{\fs10}Because that's important.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:50.13,2:15:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是因为\N{\fs10}Because what's important is that
Dialogue: 0,2:15:53.70,2:15:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们拥有彼此\N{\fs10}we have each other.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:55.50,2:15:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我们要共度一生\N{\fs10}That we have a life together.
Dialogue: 0,2:15:58.47,2:15:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会有孩子\N{\fs10}That we have children-
Dialogue: 0,2:16:00.10,2:16:01.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的孩子\N{\fs10}our children.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:02.77,2:16:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯\N{\fs10}Kay
Dialogue: 0,2:16:04.07,2:16:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我需要你\N{\fs10}I need you
Dialogue: 0,2:16:06.68,2:16:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我爱你\N{\fs10}and I love you.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:30.63,2:16:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴西尼的人抢我们的地盘\N{\fs10}Barzini's people chisel my territory
Dialogue: 0,2:16:32.67,2:16:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我们却无能为力\N{\fs10}and we do nothing about it.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:34.44,2:16:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再过不久布鲁克林连我落脚的地方都没有了\N{\fs10}Soon, there won't be one place in Brooklyn I can hang my hat.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:37.24,2:16:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有耐性点\N{\fs10}Just be patient.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:38.37,2:16:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是求你帮忙  只是不想受制肘\N{\fs10}I'm not askin' you for help. Just take off the handcuffs.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:41.34,2:16:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再忍耐点\N{\fs10}Be patient.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:42.58,2:16:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须保护自己\N{\fs10}We gotta protect ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:44.48,2:16:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我个机会再培养一些新人\N{\fs10}Give me a chance to recruit some new men.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:46.52,2:16:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fs10}No.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:48.28,2:16:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我不要给巴西尼藉口来开战  - 麦克  你错了\N{\fs10}- I don't wanna give Barzini an excuse to start fighting.- Mike, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:53.52,2:16:54.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯里昂阁下\N{\fs10}Don Corleone,
Dialogue: 0,2:16:55.76,2:16:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你曾说过要让我与泰西欧自立门户\N{\fs10}you once said the day would come when Tessio and me could form our own family.
Dialogue: 0,2:16:59.93,2:17:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天以前我想都不敢想\N{\fs10}Till today, I would never think of it.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:01.86,2:17:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在我要求你的批准\N{\fs10}I must ask your permission.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:05.00,2:17:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在由麦克当家  如果他答应我就祝福你\N{\fs10}Well, Michael is now head of the family and if he gives his permission, then you have my blessing.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:12.21,2:17:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我们搬到内华达州后\N{\fs10}After we make the move to Nevada
Dialogue: 0,2:17:14.51,2:17:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就可由柯里昂家族分出自立门户\N{\fs10}you can break off from the Corleone family and go on your own.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:17.71,2:17:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但得在我们搬到内华达州之后\N{\fs10}After we make the move to Nevada.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:19.18,2:17:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那得花多少时间？\N{\fs10}How long will that be?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:22.05,2:17:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六个月\N{\fs10}Six months.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:23.65,2:17:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原谅我  教父\N{\fs10}Forgive me, Godfather,
Dialogue: 0,2:17:24.85,2:17:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但当你走了后\N{\fs10}but with you gone
Dialogue: 0,2:17:26.62,2:17:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我与彼得迟早会成为巴西尼的靶\N{\fs10}me and Pete'll come under Barzini's thumb sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:29.96,2:17:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我恨那该死的巴西尼\N{\fs10}And I hate that goddamn Barzini.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:31.79,2:17:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六个月之后我们已经搞不出什么玩意了\N{\fs10}In six months' time, there won't be nothing left to build on.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:35.56,2:17:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你对我的判断有信心吗？\N{\fs10}You have faith in my judgment?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:37.73,2:17:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fs10}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:38.87,2:17:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你仍对我忠心吗？\N{\fs10}Do I have your loyalty?
Dialogue: 0,2:17:39.97,2:17:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  忠心不二  教父\N{\fs10}Yes, Always, Godfather.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:41.64,2:17:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么就当麦克的朋友吧\N{\fs10}Then be a friend to Michael
Dialogue: 0,2:17:43.84,2:17:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照他所说的去做\N{\fs10}and do as he says.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:49.81,2:17:51.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在有些事仍在磋商\N{\fs10}There are things being negotiated now
Dialogue: 0,2:17:51.31,2:17:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们的问题和困难全都可以得到解决\N{\fs10}that are gonna solve all your problems and answer all your questions.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:55.22,2:17:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前我只能这么说\N{\fs10}That's all I can tell you now.
Dialogue: 0,2:17:58.35,2:18:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛  你在内华达长大的\N{\fs10}Carlo, you grew up in Nevada.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:00.92,2:18:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当我们搬的时候  你会是我的左右手\N{\fs10}When we make our move there, you're gonna be my right-hand man.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:04.39,2:18:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆哈金不再做军师了\N{\fs10}Tom Hagen's no longer consigliere.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:06.93,2:18:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他将会担任我们在拉斯维加斯的律师\N{\fs10}He's gonna be our lawyer in Vegas.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:09.40,2:18:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我对汤姆没有不满  但我不要他再当军师\N{\fs10}That's no reflection on Tom, but that's the way I want it.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:11.97,2:18:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,况且有我父亲在  他可以做我最佳的军师\N{\fs10}Besides, if I ever need help who's a better consigliere than my father?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:16.17,2:18:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样了\N{\fs10}That's it.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:36.83,2:18:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 谢谢  爸爸  - 我为你高兴  卡洛\N{\fs10}- Thank you, Papa. - I'm happy for you, Carlo.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:40.80,2:18:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克  我为何出局了？\N{\fs10}Mike... Why am I out?
Dialogue: 0,2:18:44.97,2:18:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不适合当乱局中的军师\N{\fs10}You're not a wartime consigliere, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:49.04,2:18:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们一搬到内华达后  事情会变得更棘手\N{\fs10}Things may get rough with the move we're trying.
Dialogue: 0,2:18:52.44,2:18:53.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆\N{\fs10}Tom
Dialogue: 0,2:18:58.81,2:19:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向麦克建议过\N{\fs10}I advised Michael.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:01.02,2:19:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从未认为你不适合当军师\N{\fs10}I never thought you were a bad consigliere.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:04.12,2:19:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为山提诺不适合当家\N{\fs10}I thought Santino was a bad Don
Dialogue: 0,2:19:07.46,2:19:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿他安息\N{\fs10}rest in peace.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:09.66,2:19:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我信任麦克和你一样\N{\fs10}Michael has all my confidence, as you do.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:13.96,2:19:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是...\N{\fs10}But...
Dialogue: 0,2:19:15.43,2:19:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不让你参与往后的行动是有理由的\N{\fs10}there are reasons why you must have no part of what is going to happen.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:19.90,2:19:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我多少能帮得上忙\N{\fs10}Maybe I could help.
Dialogue: 0,2:19:21.64,2:19:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用不着了  汤姆\N{\fs10}- You're out, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:12.29,2:20:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我实在无法不去注意你的脸\N{\fs10}I can't get over the way your face looks.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:14.96,2:20:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它的确看起来很棒\N{\fs10}It really looks good.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:16.59,2:20:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位医生的工夫确实不错\N{\fs10}This doctor did some job.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:18.36,2:20:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是凯说服你去的吗？\N{\fs10}Who talked you into it, Kay?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:19.56,2:20:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢着  把它们留下这\N{\fs10}Hey, hey, wait. Leave them out here.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:22.10,2:20:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们待会再处理它们\N{\fs10}We'll deal with them later.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:23.40,2:20:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他累了  他想梳洗一下\N{\fs10}He's tired. He wants to clean up.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:24.90,2:20:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了  让我来开门  好吗？\N{\fs10}Now, let me open the door.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:34.21,2:20:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克  欢迎光临拉斯维加斯\N{\fs10}Hello, Mike. Welcome to Las Vegas.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:36.18,2:20:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为如何？\N{\fs10}All for you, kid.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:37.38,2:20:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全是他的主意  对吧？\N{\fs10}It was all his idea, right?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:39.41,2:20:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的哥哥弗雷多\N{\fs10}Well, your brother, Freddy-
Dialogue: 0,2:20:40.68,2:20:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你弄来的女孩子  不是吗？\N{\fs10}It was Girls?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:46.15,2:20:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我马上回来  你先招呼一下\N{\fs10}I'll be right back. You keep them occupied.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:50.43,2:20:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你要什么全都有  - 那些女孩子是谁？\N{\fs10}- That a boy. Anything you want, kid.- Who are the girls?
Dialogue: 0,2:20:55.33,2:20:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这得要你自己去弄清楚了\N{\fs10}That's for you to find out.
Dialogue: 0,2:20:57.23,2:20:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把她们弄走  弗雷多\N{\fs10}- Get rid of them, Fredo.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:00.00,2:21:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克\N{\fs10}Hey, Mike-
Dialogue: 0,2:21:01.14,2:21:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷多  我是来这公干\N{\fs10}Fredo, I'm here on business.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:02.47,2:21:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明天就走  现在把她们弄走\N{\fs10}I leave tomorrow. Now, get rid of them.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:05.17,2:21:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我累了  把乐队也弄走\N{\fs10}I'm tired. Get rid of the band too.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:13.52,2:21:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  走就对了\N{\fs10}Hey, just take off. Come on. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:16.99,2:21:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点  安琪拉  快走\N{\fs10}Hey, that's it. Angelo, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:20.72,2:21:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  闪了\N{\fs10}Let's go. Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,2:21:24.43,2:21:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  亲爱的  走了\N{\fs10}Scram! Come on, honey. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:25.53,2:21:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道  强尼\N{\fs10}I don't know,Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:26.59,2:21:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道他是怎么回事对不起\N{\fs10}I don't know what the hell's the matter with him.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:29.26,2:21:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  弗雷多\N{\fs10}It's all right, Freddy.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:31.40,2:21:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  亲爱的我不知道  他大概累了\N{\fs10}I don't know. He's tired, he's hot.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:41.08,2:21:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫格林呢？\N{\fs10}What happened to Moe Greene?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:44.15,2:21:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说他有别的事\N{\fs10}He said he had some business.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:45.55,2:21:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说派对开始时  给他个电话\N{\fs10}He said give him a call when the party started.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:48.68,2:21:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就打电话给他\N{\fs10}Well, give him a call.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:51.69,2:21:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强尼  你好吗？\N{\fs10}- Johnny, how are you?
Dialogue: 0,2:21:53.19,2:21:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克  再看到你真高兴\N{\fs10}Hello. Nice to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:55.16,2:21:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们全都以你为傲\N{\fs10}We're all proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:56.46,2:21:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  麦克\N{\fs10}Thanks, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:57.63,2:21:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐  强尼  我要跟你谈谈\N{\fs10}Sit down,Johnny. I want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,2:21:59.66,2:22:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教父也以你为傲  强尼\N{\fs10}The Don's proud of you too, Johnny.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:01.20,2:22:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的一切都归功于他\N{\fs10}I owe it all to him.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:04.27,2:22:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他知道你会感恩\N{\fs10}Well, he knows how grateful you are.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:06.13,2:22:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以他想请你帮个忙\N{\fs10}That's why he'd like to ask a favor of you.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:09.40,2:22:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克  我能做些什么？\N{\fs10}Mike, what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:12.71,2:22:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯里昂家族想放弃橄榄油的生意\N{\fs10}The Corleone family is thinking of giving up all its interests in the olive oil business,
Dialogue: 0,2:22:16.71,2:22:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而在这里安顿下来\N{\fs10}settling out here.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:18.85,2:22:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫格林会把他旅馆及赌场的股份卖给我们\N{\fs10}Now, Moe Greene will sell us his share of the casino and hotel
Dialogue: 0,2:22:22.32,2:22:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,使得家族能拥有全部的生意\N{\fs10}so it can be completely owned by the family.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:24.12,2:22:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆\N{\fs10}Tom.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:25.19,2:22:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克  这点你确定吗？\N{\fs10}Mike, are you sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,2:22:27.19,2:22:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫格林很爱这门生意\N{\fs10}Moe loves the business.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:28.42,2:22:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从未对我提过要卖掉它的事\N{\fs10}He never said nothing about selling.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:30.29,2:22:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会提个他无法拒绝的条件\N{\fs10}I'll make him an offer he can't refuse.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:34.30,2:22:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吗？强尼...\N{\fs10}See,Johnny
Dialogue: 0,2:22:36.77,2:22:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们认为表演一定可以吸引赌客到赌场来\N{\fs10}we figure that entertainment will be a big factor in drawing gamblers to the casino.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:41.10,2:22:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们希望你签个合约一年来此登台五次\N{\fs10}We hope you'll sign a contract to appear five times a year.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:47.71,2:22:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许...\N{\fs10}Perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,2:22:49.51,2:22:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顺便找些你电影圈中的朋友\N{\fs10}convince some of your friends in the movies to do the same.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:53.68,2:22:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我指望你了\N{\fs10}We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:57.72,2:22:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然  麦克\N{\fs10}Sure, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,2:22:59.09,2:23:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了教父我什么都肯做  你晓得的\N{\fs10}I'll do anything for my godfather. You know that.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:01.82,2:23:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fs10}Good.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:04.53,2:23:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克  各位好  大家都在这\N{\fs10}Hey, Mike! Hello, fellows. Everybody's here.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:07.16,2:23:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷多  汤姆...\N{\fs10}Freddy, Tom.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:09.33,2:23:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 见到你真好  麦克  - 你好吗？莫\N{\fs10}Good to see you, Mike. How are you, Moe?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:11.47,2:23:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你点的都到齐了吗？\N{\fs10}You got everything you want?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:12.70,2:23:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大厨会为你煮最好吃的菜还有最棒的舞群\N{\fs10}The chef cooked for you special, the dancers will kick your tongue out and your credit is good.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:16.74,2:23:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给房间里的每个人都弄点筹码来\N{\fs10}Draw chips for everybody in the room
Dialogue: 0,2:23:18.31,2:23:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好让他们到场子里去玩玩\N{\fs10}so they can play on the house.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:23.14,2:23:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的信用好的够买下你的股份吗？\N{\fs10}My credit good enough to buy you out?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:27.25,2:23:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,买我的股份？\N{\fs10}Buy me out?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:29.62,2:23:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赌场  这家旅馆\N{\fs10}The casino. The hotel.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:32.35,2:23:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯里昂家族想买下你全部的生意\N{\fs10}The Corleone family wants to buy you out.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:35.16,2:23:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯里昂家族想买下我全部的生意？\N{\fs10}The Corleone family wants to buy me out?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:38.29,2:23:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  我买下你们的你不能买下我的\N{\fs10}No, I buy you out. You don't buy me out.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:40.90,2:23:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的赌场在赔钱\N{\fs10}Your casino loses money.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:42.63,2:23:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许我们能经营的好一点\N{\fs10}Maybe we can do better.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:44.30,2:23:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认为我在走下坡了？麦克\N{\fs10}You think I'm skimming off the top, Mike?
Dialogue: 0,2:23:47.47,2:23:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你运气不好\N{\fs10}You're unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:53.04,2:23:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你他妈的别让我笑了\N{\fs10}You goddamn guineas really make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:55.61,2:23:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在你们有难时\N{\fs10}I do you a favor and
Dialogue: 0,2:23:56.78,2:23:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我帮你们的忙给弗雷多一份差事\N{\fs10}take Freddy in when you're having a bad time.
Dialogue: 0,2:23:58.48,2:23:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在你想把我弄出去\N{\fs10}- Then you try to push me out!
Dialogue: 0,2:23:59.98,2:24:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢着\N{\fs10}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:01.38,2:24:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你让弗雷多来这\N{\fs10}You took Freddy in
Dialogue: 0,2:24:02.62,2:24:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因为柯里昂家族支援你的赌场\N{\fs10}because the Corleone family bankrolled your casino
Dialogue: 0,2:24:05.09,2:24:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为海岸的莫伦纳家族\N{\fs10}because the Molinari family on the coast
Dialogue: 0,2:24:06.89,2:24:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,保证他的安全\N{\fs10}guaranteed his safety.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:08.39,2:24:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们在谈生意别岔开话题\N{\fs10}Now, we're talkin' business. Let's talk business.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:10.46,2:24:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好  我们来谈生意  麦克\N{\fs10}Let's talk business, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:11.83,2:24:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先  你们都完蛋了\N{\fs10}First of all, you're all done.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:13.19,2:24:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯里昂家族已经衰退了\N{\fs10}The Corleone family don't have that kind of muscle anymore.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:15.50,2:24:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教父生病了  对吧？\N{\fs10}The Godfather's sick.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:17.27,2:24:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们被巴西尼及其他家族赶出了纽约\N{\fs10}You're getting chased out of New York by Barzini and the other families.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:20.17,2:24:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这里是什么？\N{\fs10}What do you think is going on it?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:21.50,2:24:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为能到我的地盘上来接管？\N{\fs10}You think you can come to my hotel and take over?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:24.24,2:24:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和巴西尼谈过了\N{\fs10}I talked to Barzini.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:25.87,2:24:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有办法和他打交道\N{\fs10}I can make a deal with him
Dialogue: 0,2:24:27.14,2:24:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不至于失去旅馆\N{\fs10}and still keep my hotel.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:29.41,2:24:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你当众支使我哥哥？\N{\fs10}Is that why you slapped my brother around in public?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:33.15,2:24:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  麦克  那不算什么\N{\fs10}That was nothing, Mike.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:35.12,2:24:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫也不是那个意思\N{\fs10}Moe didn't mean nothing by that.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:37.82,2:24:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然他偶尔说话很大声  但是\N{\fs10}Sure he flies off the handle once in a while but
Dialogue: 0,2:24:40.29,2:24:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫和我是好朋友  对吧？莫\N{\fs10}but Moe and me, we're good friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:42.56,2:24:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是在做事业\N{\fs10}I got a business to run.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:44.26,2:24:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然要催紧点  事情才会顺利\N{\fs10}I gotta kick asses sometimes to make it run right.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:46.96,2:24:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是偶尔和弗雷多意见不合\N{\fs10}We had a little argument,
Dialogue: 0,2:24:48.53,2:24:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是为了''训练''他一下\N{\fs10}so I had to straighten him out.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:51.03,2:24:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你''训练''我哥哥？\N{\fs10}You straightened my brother out?
Dialogue: 0,2:24:53.90,2:24:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他跟酒廊的女侍鬼混\N{\fs10}He was banging cocktail waitresses two at a time!
Dialogue: 0,2:24:56.30,2:24:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,客人喝酒没人送\N{\fs10}Players couldn't get a drink.
Dialogue: 0,2:24:58.51,2:24:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么回事？\N{\fs10}What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,2:25:05.35,2:25:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明天回纽约\N{\fs10}I leave for New York tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:07.65,2:25:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你考虑一个价钱吧\N{\fs10}Think about a price.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:11.09,2:25:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我是谁吗？我是莫格林\N{\fs10}Son of a bitch. Do you know who I am? I'm Moe Greene.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:13.82,2:25:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我发迹时你还在玩泥巴\N{\fs10}I made my bones when you were going out with cheerleaders.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:16.52,2:25:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一等  莫  我有个主意\N{\fs10}Wait a minute. I got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:19.99,2:25:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆  汤姆  你是军师\N{\fs10}Tom, you're the consigliere.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:22.13,2:25:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以和教父谈  解释给他听\N{\fs10}- You can talk to the Don. You can explain
Dialogue: 0,2:25:23.73,2:25:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢着  教父已经半退休了\N{\fs10}Just a minute. Don is semi-retired and
Dialogue: 0,2:25:26.70,2:25:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家族现在由麦克管事\N{\fs10}Mike is in charge of the business now.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:28.94,2:25:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有话就向麦克说吧\N{\fs10}If you have anything to say, say it to Michael.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:36.01,2:25:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克  你不能到拉斯维加斯来\N{\fs10}Mike, You don't come to Las Vegas
Dialogue: 0,2:25:38.48,2:25:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和莫格林那种人那样说话\N{\fs10}and talk to Moe Greene like that!
Dialogue: 0,2:25:42.95,2:25:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷多\N{\fs10}Freddy.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:45.32,2:25:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是我哥  我爱你\N{\fs10}You're my older brother, and I love you.
Dialogue: 0,2:25:49.52,2:25:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但不准你再联合外人起来反对自己家族\N{\fs10}But don't ever take sides with anyone against the family again
Dialogue: 0,2:26:04.24,2:26:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我必须先去看我父亲和他的手下\N{\fs10}I have to see my father and his people.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:05.91,2:26:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们先吃饭吧\N{\fs10}Have dinner without me.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:07.48,2:26:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克\N{\fs10}Michael
Dialogue: 0,2:26:10.14,2:26:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个周末我们可以出外游玩\N{\fs10}This weekend we'll go out.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:11.55,2:26:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到城里看电影吃饭  我保证\N{\fs10}We'll go to the city. We'll see a show and have dinner. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:22.46,2:26:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克\N{\fs10}Michael
Dialogue: 0,2:26:23.59,2:26:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克  你姐姐有事想问你\N{\fs10}Your sister wants to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:25.46,2:26:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她可以问我  - 她怕你\N{\fs10}- Let her ask. - She's afraid to.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:27.66,2:26:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,康妮和卡洛要你当他们孩子的教父\N{\fs10}Connie and Carlo want you to be godfather to their little boy.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:30.70,2:26:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 到时再说吧  - 你会吗？\N{\fs10}- We'll see. - Will you?
Dialogue: 0,2:26:32.67,2:26:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我考虑一下到时再说  来吧\N{\fs10}Let me think about it. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:41.84,2:26:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴西尼想要先对付你\N{\fs10}So Barzini will move against you first.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:46.81,2:26:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会找个你信任的人来安排见面\N{\fs10}He'll set up a meeting with someone that you absolutely trust
Dialogue: 0,2:26:51.32,2:26:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并保证你的安全\N{\fs10}guaranteeing your safety.
Dialogue: 0,2:26:54.56,2:26:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你一出席会议  他就杀了你\N{\fs10}And at that meeting, you'll be assassinated.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:02.63,2:27:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在比以前爱喝酒了\N{\fs10}I like to drink wine more than I used to.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:06.87,2:27:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且越爱喝就喝的越多\N{\fs10}Anyway, I'm drinking more.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:09.20,2:27:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对你有好处的  爸爸\N{\fs10}It's good for you, Pop.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:15.51,2:27:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fs10}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:18.98,2:27:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太太和小孩过的还快乐吧？\N{\fs10}Your wife and children, are you happy with them?
Dialogue: 0,2:27:22.88,2:27:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常快乐\N{\fs10}Very happy.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:24.82,2:27:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fs10}That's good.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:27.56,2:27:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你不介意我一直在谈巴西尼\N{\fs10}I hope you don't mind the way I I keep going over this Barzini business.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:32.49,2:27:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不  一点也不\N{\fs10}No, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:34.53,2:27:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的老习惯\N{\fs10}It's an old habit.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:36.96,2:27:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我花了一辈子就学会了''小心''\N{\fs10}I spent my life tryin' not to be careless.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:41.54,2:27:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女人和小孩能够粗心大意  但男人不行\N{\fs10}Women and children can be careless, but not men.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:48.24,2:27:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你儿子还好吗？  - 很好\N{\fs10}- How's your boy? - He's good.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:50.81,2:27:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他越来越像你了\N{\fs10}You know, he looks more like you every day.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:56.25,2:27:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他比我聪明\N{\fs10}He's smarter than I am.
Dialogue: 0,2:27:58.72,2:28:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才三岁就懂得看漫画了\N{\fs10}Three years old, he can read the funny papers.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:02.76,2:28:04.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看漫画\N{\fs10}He reads the funny papers.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:12.03,2:28:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你安排一个电话公司的人\N{\fs10}I want you to arrange to have a telephone man
Dialogue: 0,2:28:14.50,2:28:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,查每一个进出这里的电话\N{\fs10}check all the calls that go in and out of here.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:17.97,2:28:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我已经做了  爸  - 任何一个人都有可能\N{\fs10}- I did it already. - Could be anyone.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:20.27,2:28:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 爸  我已经处理那件事了  - 没错  我忘了\N{\fs10}- I took care of that. - That's right. I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:27.15,2:28:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？\N{\fs10}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:29.78,2:28:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么困扰着你？\N{\fs10}What's bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,2:28:35.29,2:28:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我应付得了  我说能  我就能\N{\fs10}I'll handle it. I told you I can handle it, I'll handle it.
Dialogue: 0,2:28:53.27,2:28:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道山提诺势必会染指家族事业\N{\fs10}I knew that Santino was gonna have to go through all this
Dialogue: 0,2:28:57.78,2:28:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有弗雷多\N{\fs10}and Fredo-
Dialogue: 0,2:29:02.18,2:29:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弗雷多他...\N{\fs10}Fredo was-
Dialogue: 0,2:29:06.09,2:29:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我从来没...\N{\fs10}But I never...
Dialogue: 0,2:29:07.42,2:29:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没想到要你参与\N{\fs10} I never wanted this for you.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:11.09,2:29:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我干了一辈子  没什么遗憾的\N{\fs10}I worked my whole life- I don't apologize-
Dialogue: 0,2:29:13.39,2:29:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我照顾了我的家人\N{\fs10}to take care of my family
Dialogue: 0,2:29:16.33,2:29:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我绝不当傻瓜\N{\fs10}and I refused to be a fool
Dialogue: 0,2:29:20.33,2:29:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让那些大人物在幕后操纵我\N{\fs10}dancing on a string held by all those big shots.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:26.37,2:29:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不必道歉  那是我的命运但是我想过...\N{\fs10}I don't apologize. That's my life. But I thought that-
Dialogue: 0,2:29:31.58,2:29:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一天你能当那些操纵的人\N{\fs10}that when it was your time you would be the one to hold the strings.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:38.59,2:29:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯里昂参议员\N{\fs10}Senator Corleone.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:42.09,2:29:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柯里昂州长之类的\N{\fs10}Governor Corleone. Something.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:43.86,2:29:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再建立一个王国\N{\fs10}Another pezzonovante.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:47.43,2:29:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个... 时间不多了  麦克时间不多了\N{\fs10}Just wasn't enough time, Michael. Wasn't enough time.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:56.27,2:29:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会做到的  爸\N{\fs10}We'll get there, Pop.
Dialogue: 0,2:29:58.97,2:30:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会做到的\N{\fs10}We'll get there.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:04.65,2:30:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听好...\N{\fs10}Listen,
Dialogue: 0,2:30:05.98,2:30:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁请你去和巴西尼开会\N{\fs10}whoever comes to you with this Barzini meeting
Dialogue: 0,2:30:09.08,2:30:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他就是叛徒\N{\fs10}he's the traitor.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:10.92,2:30:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千万别忘了\N{\fs10}Don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:29.14,2:30:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能让我拿吗？
Dialogue: 0,2:30:40.58,2:30:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能自己浇水\N{\fs10}Can I water these
Dialogue: 0,2:30:46.45,2:30:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以浇水吗？\N{\fs10}- Can I water these?
Dialogue: 0,2:30:48.16,2:30:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以  浇吧\N{\fs10}- Yeah. That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:50.46,2:30:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里  来这里\N{\fs10}Over here. Over here.
Dialogue: 0,2:30:55.03,2:30:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小心点  别溅到了  小心\N{\fs10}Be careful. You're spilling it. You're spilling it.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:03.84,2:31:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安东尼  过来  来吧...\N{\fs10}Anthony, come here. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:09.01,2:31:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来这里\N{\fs10}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:11.75,2:31:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了  放在这\N{\fs10}That's right. We'll put it right there.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:20.62,2:31:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来  有东西给你看\N{\fs10}I'll show you something. Come here.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:22.92,2:31:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来这\N{\fs10}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:25.06,2:31:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你站好\N{\fs10}Now, you stand there.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:30.70,2:31:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把柳丁给我\N{\fs10}Give me an orange!
Dialogue: 0,2:31:40.14,2:31:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别怕
Dialogue: 0,2:31:50.85,2:31:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是新把戏\N{\fs10}That's a new trick.
Dialogue: 0,2:31:53.82,2:31:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你去里面  去里面\N{\fs10}You run in there. Run in there.
Dialogue: 0,2:32:09.60,2:32:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪？\N{\fs10}- Where are you? - Who?
Dialogue: 0,2:32:13.67,2:32:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倒下去\N{\fs10}Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,2:35:09.08,2:35:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克  能借一步说话吗？\N{\fs10}Mike, can I have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,2:35:21.50,2:35:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴西尼想要安排一次会议\N{\fs10}Barzini wants to arrange a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:23.83,2:35:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说任何的问题都可以谈出一个解决之道\N{\fs10}He says we can straighten any of our problems out.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:28.14,2:35:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你和他谈过了？  - 是的\N{\fs10}- You talked to him? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:31.54,2:35:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能安排安全事宜\N{\fs10}I can arrange security
Dialogue: 0,2:35:34.14,2:35:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我的地盘上  好吗？\N{\fs10}on my territory. All right?
Dialogue: 0,2:35:40.51,2:35:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 好的  - 好\N{\fs10}- All right. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,2:35:58.60,2:36:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他们预备怎么对付你吗？\N{\fs10}Do you know how they're gonna come at you?
Dialogue: 0,2:36:04.10,2:36:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们安排在布鲁克林开会\N{\fs10}They're arranging a meeting in Brooklyn.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:06.51,2:36:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰西欧的地盘上\N{\fs10}Tessio's ground
Dialogue: 0,2:36:09.81,2:36:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说在那我会安全的\N{\fs10}where I'll be safe.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:23.89,2:36:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以为是克里曼沙  没想到是泰西欧\N{\fs10}I always thought it would've been Clemenza, not Tessio.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:27.63,2:36:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一招漂亮  泰西欧一向聪明\N{\fs10}It's the smart move. Tessio was always smarter.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:33.70,2:36:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我会静观其变\N{\fs10}But I'm gonna wait.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:36.27,2:36:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等洗礼过了再说\N{\fs10}After the baptism.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:40.44,2:36:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我决定当康妮小孩的教父了\N{\fs10}I've decided to be godfather to Connie's baby.
Dialogue: 0,2:36:44.41,2:36:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后我再去见巴西尼\N{\fs10}And then I'll meet with Don Barzini
Dialogue: 0,2:36:47.48,2:36:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有塔塔基利亚\N{\fs10}and Tattaglia
Dialogue: 0,2:36:49.85,2:36:52.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有五大家族的族长\N{\fs10}all the heads of the five families.
Dialogue: 0,2:37:18.98,2:37:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（意大利文祷词）
Dialogue: 0,2:37:29.62,2:37:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿门\N{\fs10}Amen!
Dialogue: 0,2:37:32.09,2:37:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（意大利文祷词）
Dialogue: 0,2:39:13.63,2:39:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克  你相信上帝吗？\N{\fs10}Michael, do you believe in God,
Dialogue: 0,2:39:15.00,2:39:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全能的天父  万物的创造者\N{\fs10}the Father Almighty creator of Heaven and Earth?
Dialogue: 0,2:39:18.83,2:39:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信\N{\fs10}I do.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:20.07,2:39:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你相信耶稣基督他的独子  我们的主吗？\N{\fs10}Do you believe in Jesus Christ, his only Son, our Lord?
Dialogue: 0,2:39:23.47,2:39:24.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信\N{\fs10}I do.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:24.67,2:39:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你相信圣灵  神圣的教堂吗？\N{\fs10}Do you believe in the holy Ghost, the holy Catholic Church?
Dialogue: 0,2:39:28.84,2:39:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我相信\N{\fs10}I do.
Dialogue: 0,2:39:30.28,2:39:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（意大利文祷词）
Dialogue: 0,2:40:35.68,2:40:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克柯里昂\N{\fs10}Michael Francis Rizzi,
Dialogue: 0,2:40:37.91,2:40:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你弃绝撒旦吗？\N{\fs10}do you renounce Satan?
Dialogue: 0,2:40:46.39,2:40:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我弃绝\N{\fs10}I do renounce him.
Dialogue: 0,2:40:57.50,2:40:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包括他所有的作为吗？\N{\fs10}And all his works?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:12.61,2:41:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我弃绝\N{\fs10}I do renounce them.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:19.55,2:41:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包括他所有的虚伪？\N{\fs10}- And all his pomps?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:21.76,2:41:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我弃绝\N{\fs10}I do renounce them.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:39.01,2:41:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克柯里昂\N{\fs10}Michael Rizzi,
Dialogue: 0,2:41:41.17,2:41:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意当他的教父吗？\N{\fs10}will you be baptized?
Dialogue: 0,2:41:43.21,2:41:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愿意\N{\fs10}I will.
Dialogue: 0,2:41:44.75,2:41:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（意大利文祷词）
Dialogue: 0,2:41:51.85,2:41:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克柯里昂\N{\fs10}Michael Rizzi
Dialogue: 0,2:41:53.59,2:41:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿主与你同在  阿门\N{\fs10}Go in peace, and may the Lord be with you. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:11.10,2:42:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯\N{\fs10}Kay.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:13.47,2:42:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的教父\N{\fs10}This is your godfather.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:39.73,2:42:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 卡洛  - 什么事\N{\fs10}- Carlo. - What?
Dialogue: 0,2:42:41.77,2:42:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在不能去拉斯维加斯\N{\fs10}Can't go to Vegas.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:43.20,2:42:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,临时有要事  让他们先走吧\N{\fs10}Something's come up.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:45.81,2:42:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 麦克  这是我们第一次度假  - 康妮  别吵\N{\fs10}- It's our first vacation together. - Connie, please.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:48.54,2:42:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你要我怎么做  - 回家去等我电话  有要事\N{\fs10}- What do you wanna do? - Go back to the house. Wait for my call. It's important.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:51.58,2:42:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fs10}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:53.61,2:42:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只需一两天\N{\fs10}I'll only be a couple of days.
Dialogue: 0,2:42:58.59,2:43:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旅途愉快  妈\N{\fs10}Have a nice trip, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:12.13,2:43:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去布鲁克林了\N{\fs10}We're on our way to Brooklyn.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:16.40,2:43:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望麦克今晚能谈个好交易\N{\fs10}I hope Mike can get us a good deal tonight.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:18.87,2:43:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他一定会的\N{\fs10}I'm sure he will.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:28.08,2:43:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙尔  汤姆\N{\fs10}Sal, Tom,
Dialogue: 0,2:43:29.38,2:43:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老板说他自己坐车来\N{\fs10}the boss says he'll come in a separate car.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:31.25,2:43:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫你们先走\N{\fs10}He says for you two to go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:33.35,2:43:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不能那么做\N{\fs10}He can't do that.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:34.49,2:43:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 弄乱了我所有的安排  - 他是这么说的\N{\fs10}It screws up all my arrangements. That's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:37.19,2:43:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不能去  沙尔\N{\fs10}I can't go either, Sal.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:51.20,2:43:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉麦克这纯粹是生意\N{\fs10}Tell Mike it was only business.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:54.07,2:43:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都喜欢他\N{\fs10}I always liked him.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:56.64,2:43:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会了解的  沙尔\N{\fs10}He understands that.
Dialogue: 0,2:43:57.84,2:43:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  沙尔\N{\fs10}Excuse me, Sal.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:05.79,2:44:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆  能替我求个情吗？\N{\fs10}Can you get me off the hook?
Dialogue: 0,2:44:09.29,2:44:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 看在老交情的份上  - 我做不到  沙尔\N{\fs10}- For old times' sake. - Can't do it, Sally.
Dialogue: 0,2:44:57.97,2:45:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你得为山尼的事偿命  卡洛\N{\fs10}You have to answer for Santino, Carlo.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:05.71,2:45:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你误会了  麦克  - 你为巴西尼的人设计害山尼\N{\fs10}You got it all wrong. You fingered Sonny for the Barzini people.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:10.62,2:45:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和我姐姐演的那场闹剧\N{\fs10}That little farce you played with my sister.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:14.52,2:45:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以为骗得过柯里昂家的人吗？\N{\fs10}Did you think that could fool a Corleone?
Dialogue: 0,2:45:16.49,2:45:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克  我是清白的\N{\fs10}I'm innocent.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:17.86,2:45:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以我的孩子来发誓\N{\fs10}I swear on the kids.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:19.63,2:45:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 求你  麦克  别这样对我  - 坐下\N{\fs10}- Please, don't do this to me. - Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:25.33,2:45:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克  别这样对我  求你\N{\fs10}Don't do this to me, please.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:36.78,2:45:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴西尼死了\N{\fs10}Barzini's dead.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:40.41,2:45:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,菲立浦塔塔基利亚也死了\N{\fs10}So is Phillip Tattaglia
Dialogue: 0,2:45:44.15,2:45:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有莫格林  史特基克里安诺\N{\fs10}Moe Greene Strachi Cuneo.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:52.06,2:45:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天我一次清理整个家族的事\N{\fs10}Today I settle all family business,
Dialogue: 0,2:45:53.86,2:45:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以别跟我说你是无辜的  卡洛\N{\fs10}so don't tell me you're innocent.
Dialogue: 0,2:45:57.66,2:45:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,承认你所做过的\N{\fs10}Admit what you did.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:03.34,2:46:04.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给他一杯酒\N{\fs10}Get him a drink.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:11.48,2:46:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说吧\N{\fs10}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:13.88,2:46:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别怕  卡洛\N{\fs10}Don't be afraid, Carlo.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:16.35,2:46:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我忍心让我姐姐当寡妇？\N{\fs10}You think I'd make my sister a widow?
Dialogue: 0,2:46:20.39,2:46:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我又是你儿子的教父  卡洛\N{\fs10}I'm godfather to your son, Carlo.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:30.06,2:46:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝吧\N{\fs10}Go ahead, drink.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:36.97,2:46:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛  从此你退出家族的生意  这是给你的惩罚\N{\fs10}No, you're out of the family business. That's your punishment.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:41.81,2:46:45.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你玩完了  我送你上飞机去拉斯维加斯\N{\fs10}You're finished. I'm putting you on a plane to Vegas.
Dialogue: 0,2:46:45.85,2:46:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,汤姆\N{\fs10}Tom
Dialogue: 0,2:46:51.65,2:46:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要你留在那边  明白吗？\N{\fs10}I want you to stay there. Understand?
Dialogue: 0,2:46:55.29,2:46:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是别告诉我你是无辜的\N{\fs10}Only don't tell me you're innocent
Dialogue: 0,2:46:59.26,2:47:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为那等于把我当傻瓜\N{\fs10}because it insults my intelligence.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:02.33,2:47:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会让我非常生气\N{\fs10}It makes me very angry.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:07.67,2:47:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在  是谁和你接头的？\N{\fs10}Now, who approached you?
Dialogue: 0,2:47:10.97,2:47:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔塔基利亚还是巴西尼？\N{\fs10}Tattaglia or Barzini?
Dialogue: 0,2:47:21.15,2:47:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是巴西尼\N{\fs10}It was Barzini.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:27.09,2:47:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fs10}Good.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:34.76,2:47:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外面有辆车等着送你去机场\N{\fs10}There's a car waiting for you outside to take you to the airport.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:38.83,2:47:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我通知你太太  说你坐那班飞机\N{\fs10}I'll call your wife, tell her what flight you're on.
Dialogue: 0,2:47:46.87,2:47:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 麦克  我...   - 快走  别让我看到你\N{\fs10}- Please, can I- - Get out of my sight.
Dialogue: 0,2:48:15.47,2:48:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛\N{\fs10}Hello, Carlo.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:14.86,2:49:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想告诉我什么？\N{\fs10}Will you stop crying? What are you trying to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,2:49:16.96,2:49:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我想告诉你...   - 妈妈  拜托...\N{\fs10}- I'm telling you you're wrong. - Mama, please!
Dialogue: 0,2:49:28.38,2:49:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克...\N{\fs10}Michael
Dialogue: 0,2:49:30.64,2:49:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 怎么了？  - 他在哪儿？麦克\N{\fs10}Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,2:49:35.05,2:49:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麦克  你这混蛋你杀了我丈夫\N{\fs10}Michael, you lousy bastard! You killed my husband!
Dialogue: 0,2:49:40.09,2:49:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看爸一死  就没人能管你了\N{\fs10}You waited until Papa died so nobody could stop you
Dialogue: 0,2:49:42.79,2:49:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就把他杀了\N{\fs10}and then you killed him!
Dialogue: 0,2:49:44.29,2:49:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直把山尼的死怪在他身上\N{\fs10}You blamed him for Sonny.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:45.99,2:49:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直如此  大家都如此\N{\fs10}You always did. Everybody did.
Dialogue: 0,2:49:47.43,2:49:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你有没有想过我？\N{\fs10}But you never thought about me!
Dialogue: 0,2:49:49.30,2:49:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从来不在乎我\N{\fs10}You never gave a damn about me!
Dialogue: 0,2:49:51.33,2:49:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我以后要怎么办？\N{\fs10}Now what am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,2:49:53.43,2:49:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,康妮...\N{\fs10}Connie
Dialogue: 0,2:49:57.37,2:49:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为他为何要卡洛在他身边\N{\fs10}Why do you think he kept Carlo at the mall?
Dialogue: 0,2:50:00.07,2:50:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他早就算计好要杀他\N{\fs10}All the time he knew he was gonna kill him.
